NK100(the)011:1: // stobs gsum gyi man ngag thugs snying gi gsal byed bzhugs //
NK100(the)011:2: blang dor gnyis med kun bzang chos kyi sku //
NK100(the)011:3: ngo bo ma 'gags longs sku rdo rje sems //
NK100(the)011:4: thugs rje don mdzad dga' rab sprul pa'i sku //
NK100(the)011:5: gsum las rim brgyud rigs 'dzin bzhad pa rtsal //
NK100(the)011:6: rim par brgyud nas 'gro mgon zhig po la //
NK100(the)011:7: bzhi ldan bka' babs sprul sku rin po che //
NK100(the)011:8: drin can bla ma'i brgyud pa'i zhabs rdul la //
NK100(the)011:9: lus gus ngag dang gnyis med yid kyis 'dud //
NK100(the)011:11: gnas lugs lhun grub ye shes sangs rgyas pa de /
NK100(the)011:12: kun la rang chas gnas te rtags chen nyi shu ldan /
NK100(the)011:13: ma shes kun tu brtags pas khams gsum 'khor bar 'khyams /
NK100(the)011:14: gnas lugs ngo sprad gdams ngag rdo rje bzhad las brgyud /
NK100(the)011:15: stobs gsum 'dren pa'i gdams ngag snyan rgyud thugs snying la /
NK100(the)011:16: bdag gzhan don du gsung 'gros rjed thor bri bar bya /
NK100(the)011:18: don gyi rdzogs pa chen po rang sems stong gsal
NK100(the)011:19: gnyis med chos kyi sku rang chas su gnas pa
NK100(the)011:20: la / rang gsal thabs kyis chod pa de mtshon
NK100(the)011:21: byed tshig gi rdzogs pa chen pos ngo sprod byed
NK100(the)011:22: la / tsam na / rdzogs chen gdams ngag stobs gsum gyis //
NK100(the)011:23: gdul bya rnam gsum drangs pa'i phyir //
NK100(the)011:24: ston pa gsum gyis gsungs pa bzhin //
NK100(the)011:25: phyi rabs drangs phyir bshad par bya //
NK100(the)011:27: rdzogs chen gdams ngag stobs gsum gyis zhes pas /
NK100(the)011:28: bshad pa'i stobs dang gcig /brtsod pa'i stobs dang gnyis /
NK100(the)011:29: sgrub pa'i stobs dang gsum gyis /
NK100(the)011:30: 'o na des ci byed ce na /
NK100(the)011:31: gdul bya rnam gsum drangs pa'i phyir zhes pas /
NK100(the)011:32: bshad pa la mos pa'i gdul bya /
NK100(the)011:33: brtsod pa'i la mos pa'i gdul bya /
NK100(the)011:34: sgrub pa la mos pa'i gdul bya gsum drangs pa'i phyir ro //
NK100(the)011:35: 'o na de rang bzo min nam zhe na /
NK100(the)011:36: ston pa gsum gyis gsung pa bzhin /
NK100(the)011:37: zhes pas rang bzo min te /
NK100(the)011:38: chos sku kun tu bzang po dang /
NK100(the)011:39: longs sku rdo rje sems dpa' dang /
NK100(the)011:40: sprul sku dga' rab rdo rje gsum gyis gsungs pa bzhin du /
NK100(the)011:41: phyi rabs mos pa rnams drangs par bya'o zhes so //
NK100(the)011:43: gdul bya gzhung bshad pa la mos pa gcig 'dug na /
NK100(the)011:44: gdams ngag gi 'dren sgo yang gzhung bshad pa'i dbang du byas te /
NK100(the)011:45: dkyus dgrol ba'i gdams ngag ni stobs kyis drangs dang
NK100(the)011:46: gcig /gdul bya rgol phyir rgol brtsod pa la mos
NK100(the)011:48: gdams ngag ni 'dren sgo yang rgol phyir rgol brtsod pa bzlog pa'i dbang du byas te /
NK100(the)011:49: skyon bsal ba'i gdams ngag gi stobs kyis drong pa
NK100(the)011:50: dang gnyis gdul bya byang chub sgrub pa la mos
NK100(the)011:52: gdams ngag gi 'dren sgo yang byang chub sgrub pa'i dbang du byas te /
NK100(the)011:53: nyams su blangs pa'i gdams ngag gi stobs kyis drang pa dang gsum mo //
NK100(the)011:54: de yang gzhung bshad pa la drug ste bgrang /
NK100(the)011:55: dkyus kyi khog gzhung la mkhas par bya ba'i phyir na /
NK100(the)011:56: khog dbub pa'i gzhung ni rgyud thams cad phun sum tshogs pa lnga'i sgo nas khog dbub /
NK100(the)011:57: bstan bcos thams cad rtsis 'go lnga'i sgo nas khog 'bubs /
NK100(the)011:58: man ngag phal cher dgos don rnam pa lnga'i sgo nas khog phub nas /
NK100(the)011:60: stong thun tu na ma 'ga' yar drangs nas ston pa de yin /
NK100(the)011:61: de la mkhas na yang mkhas pa sna cig tu 'gro /
NK100(the)011:62: dkyus kyi rnam dbye la mkhas par bya ba'i phyir na /
NK100(the)011:63: sa bcad pa'i gdams ngag /spyir chos tshoms su phye nas ming re 'dogs pa de yin /
NK100(the)011:64: de la gsum las bka' rang lugs ni /
NK100(the)011:65: rgyud la le'u man ngag la skabs su ston pas dang po rang nas phye ba de'o //
NK100(the)011:66: slob dpon gdams ngag gis gcod ni /
NK100(the)011:69: 'jug dang de las na tshogs su gong ma rnams kyis phye ba de'o //
NK100(the)011:70: 'chad mkhan rigs pa ni gong nas phye ba med kyang /
NK100(the)011:71: spyir bstan bye brag tu bstan pa la sogs pa 'am /
NK100(the)011:72: 'bru'i 'dug sa bsgyur ba la sogs pa'o //
NK100(the)011:73: dkyus kyi ngo ti la mkhas par bya phyir ni /
NK100(the)011:75: bshad grags pa dang ma shod pa'i 'bru dgur du lus pa med par /
NK100(the)011:76: tshig gi mdud pa khrol ba /
NK100(the)011:77: don gyi go ba longs pa /
NK100(the)011:78: 'bru pas dang kyis la sogs pa ma lus pa'o //
NK100(the)011:79: dkyus kyi rgal len la mkhas par bya ba'i phyir ni /
NK100(the)011:80: dri ba lan gyi gdams ngag ni /
NK100(the)011:81: phas rgal ba'i lan tshul 'debs pa mkhas pa ste /
NK100(the)011:83: 'gal rkyen la sogs pa phas rgal ba'i lan tshus 'debs pa la mkhas pa'o //
NK100(the)011:84: dkyus kyi 'gro so la mkhas par bya ba'i phyir na /
NK100(the)011:85: mthar thug grub mtha'i gdams ngag ni /
NK100(the)011:90: don gyi 'gro sa 'am go ba 'di las med ces bya'o //
NK100(the)011:91: dkyus kyi nyams blangs pa la mkhas par bya ba'i phyir na /
NK100(the)011:92: lam du blangs pa'i gdams ngag ni /
NK100(the)011:93: gong ma ltar bshad nas kyang /
NK100(the)011:94: mtshan bcas mtshan med dam lta bsgom spyod pa la
NK100(the)011:95: sogs pa'i sgo nas nyams su 'di ltar len pa'o
NK100(the)011:96: // de rnams re re la mkhas kyang mkhas pa sna re yin la /
NK100(the)011:97: kun la mkhas na mkhas pa chen po'o //
NK100(the)011:98: don go gi dril bas gzhung gi nyan bshad ci tsam byas kyang sangs rgya ba las med /
NK100(the)011:99: sangs rgya ba la zhen pa dang 'dzin pa grol dgos pas /
NK100(the)011:100: nyan shad mkhan po tsho zhen pa dang 'dzin pa
NK100(the)011:101: grol lam ma grol lta rtog thong gsum gsung ngo
NK100(the)011:102: // rgol phyir rgol rtsod pa la drug ste bsgrang /
NK100(the)011:103: chos can ni gtan la dbab bya'i yul yin te /
NK100(the)011:104: brtsod pa'i dus su mthun snang /
NK100(the)011:105: tshogs la bshad pa'i dus su zhen snang /
NK100(the)011:106: slob bu lam du slong ba'i dus su tshogs brgyad yul dang bcas pa chos can du 'jog pa'o //
NK100(the)011:107: dam bca' ni skabs kyi stobs kyis bsgrub bya nyid du khas blangs pa'o //
NK100(the)011:108: gtan tshigs ni dam baca'i don gtan la 'bebs par byed pa ni yin te /
NK100(the)011:109: mtshan nyid pa la mu bzhi skye 'gog dang /
NK100(the)011:111: rdo rje gzegs ma la sogs pa'o //
NK100(the)011:112: gsang sngags pa ni sgra mthun don spags dang /
NK100(the)011:113: tshad ma bka' gzhung la sogs pa'o //
NK100(the)011:114: a ti'i skabs 'dir skye 'gag gnyis med yin te /
NK100(the)011:115: de yang 'dir ngang skye ba med pa'i gtan tshigs kyis mtshon /
NK100(the)011:116: ngos bzung dang bral bar gtan la 'bebs /
NK100(the)011:117: rang bzhin 'gag med rang snang du /
NK100(the)011:118: bdag nyid gnyis med du gtan la 'bebs pa'o //
NK100(the)011:119: thal 'gyur ni pha rol mi rigs pa'i khas len na gnod byed kyi skyon btang nas bshis pa'o //
NK100(the)011:120: 'dod thog ni rang dam bcas pa dang skyon btang pa mtshungs pa'o //
NK100(the)011:121: bsal pa ni 'dod thog ma yin pa la 'dod
NK100(the)011:122: thog tu byung nas bsal pa gtong pa yin te
NK100(the)011:126: rang tshigs gis bsal pa la sogs pa'o //
NK100(the)011:127: de yang 'dir sems nyid yin lugs kho na la mtshon te /
NK100(the)011:128: ka ba lta bu'i zhen snang 'di chos can /
NK100(the)011:129: sems nyid rang snang yin te zhes bya bar dam bca' /
NK100(the)011:130: skye 'gag gnyis su med pa'i phyir rol sogs pa yin lugs bzhin du sgrub bo //
NK100(the)011:132: da res 'dir byang chub sgrub pa gtsor ston /
NK100(the)011:133: de yang 'khor ba'i snang tshul 'di dag me mar
NK100(the)011:134: mo'i 'obs bzhin sdug bsngal gyi rgya mtshor mthong ste
NK100(the)011:135: / thar pa sgrub pa'i gang zag la bstan no //
NK100(the)011:137: thun mong spyi'i gdams ngag ni /
NK100(the)011:138: so so skye bo grub mtha' blo bsgyur nas /
NK100(the)011:139: a ti'i sgor zhugs pa'i dge ba'i bshes gnyen man chad kun la dgos kyang dgos /
NK100(the)011:140: kun gyis go yang go bas de skad ces bya'o //
NK100(the)011:141: khyad par rang gzhung gi gdams ngag ni thun mong
NK100(the)011:142: spyi las khyad par du byas nas rdzogs pa chen
NK100(the)011:143: po rang gi gzhung gzhi lam 'bras gsum du gril
NK100(the)011:144: nas ston pa'o // bsdu ba 'jug gi gdams ngag
NK100(the)011:145: ni gong du bshad pa la nyams myong 'di lta
NK100(the)011:146: nas ston pa'o // bu skye'o // che ba 'di dang ldan no //
NK100(the)011:147: gdams ngag tshig dgur bsdus nas ston pa la de skad ces bya'o //
NK100(the)011:148: dang po la gnyis te bsgrang /
NK100(the)011:149: de'i dang po la gsum ste bsgrang /
NK100(the)011:150: chos byed pa la sngon 'gror thog mar dal 'byor thob dgos pas dang por dal 'byor brtag pa /
NK100(the)011:151: dal 'byor can chos sgor 'jug pa la dad pa dgos pa bar du dad pa bskyed pa /
NK100(the)011:152: dad pa can lam sna 'dren pa la bla ma dgos pas tha mar bla ma brten pa'o //
NK100(the)011:153: dang po dal 'byor brtag pa gsum bsgrang /
NK100(the)011:154: dang po dal ba brtag pa ni /
NK100(the)011:155: las byar med pa dal lam zhe na ma yin te /
NK100(the)011:156: ma nyams pa bdun dang ldan pa'o //
NK100(the)011:157: de la brten nas nyams pa ni /
NK100(the)011:158: de'i bzlog pa bcad pa ni /
NK100(the)011:159: rten nyams pa ni ngan song gsum gyi sems can no //
NK100(the)011:160: de ci'i phyir nyams na dmyal ba tsha grang gi sdug bsngal gyis brel /
NK100(the)011:162: byol song glen lkugs kyi sdug bsngal gyis brel te /
NK100(the)011:163: sdig pa rang bzhin gyis sog /dge ba bya thabs med pas rten nyams pa'o //
NK100(the)011:164: ma nyams pa gang zhe na /
NK100(the)011:165: rten gyi dal ba phun sum 'tshogs pa zhes bya ba mi lus so //
NK100(the)011:166: de ci'i phyir zhe na dge ba spyad du yod pas so //
NK100(the)011:167: des chog gam zhe na mi chog ste /
NK100(the)011:168: gling ma nyams pa cig dgos so //
NK100(the)011:169: de'i bzlog pa bcad de nyams pa gang zhe na /
NK100(the)011:170: gling chen po gsum dang gling phran brgyad ni /
NK100(the)011:178: rnga yab dang ni rnga yab gzhan /
NK100(the)011:179: g.yo ldan dang ni lam mchog 'gro /
NK100(the)011:180: sgra mi snyan dang sgra mi snyan gyi zla'o //
NK100(the)011:181: de ci'i phyir zhe na chos med pas so //
NK100(the)011:185: de ci'i phyir zhen dus gsum sangs rgyas kyi byon
NK100(the)011:186: pa chos kyi 'khor lo bskor ba yin pas so
NK100(the)011:187: // de ni gling gi dal ba'o //
NK100(the)011:189: 'o na des chog gam zhe na mi chog ste /
NK100(the)011:190: gnas gzhan ma nyams pa gcig dgos so //
NK100(the)011:191: de'i zlog pa bcad de nyams pa gang zhe na /
NK100(the)011:194: 'bog chor gyi sde la sogs pa'o //
NK100(the)011:196: dkon mchog gsum gyi sgra mi grags /
NK100(the)011:197: sdig pa rang bzhin gyis sog pas so //
NK100(the)011:198: ma nyams pa gang zhe na /
NK100(the)011:199: rgya gar rdo rje gdan nam bod ba zal mo'i sgang la sogs pa'o //
NK100(the)011:200: ci'i phyir na dkon mchog gsum la dad gus byed /
NK100(the)011:201: chos nyams su blang du yod /
NK100(the)011:202: dus gsum sangs rgyas dang grub thob kun gyi 'byung gnas yin pas so //
NK100(the)011:203: des chog gam zhe na mi chog ste /
NK100(the)011:204: dbang po ma nyams pa cig dgos so //
NK100(the)011:207: 'on dig long pa la sogs pa'o //
NK100(the)011:209: rna ba 'on na chos mi thob /
NK100(the)011:211: lkugs na sgra mi shes pas so //
NK100(the)011:212: 'o na de nyung ngam bsno blo don gyi dbang po lnga nyams te /
NK100(the)011:213: la la dad pa'i dbang po nyams te chos la mi mos /
NK100(the)011:214: la la brtson 'grus kyi dbang po nyams te le lo che /
NK100(the)011:215: la la dran pa'i dbang po nyams te zin pa dang rjed pa gang rkyen cha med /
NK100(the)011:216: la la ting nge 'dzin gyi dbang po nyams te lta bsgom mi gsal /
NK100(the)011:217: la la shes rab kyi dbang po nyams te chos kyi don mi go //
NK100(the)011:218: ma nyams dbang po skyon med do //
NK100(the)011:219: de ci'i phyir na nyan pa dang lta ba dang
NK100(the)011:220: kha thon pa la sogs par byar yod pa'i phyir
NK100(the)011:221: ro // don gyi ma nyams pa ni go sla'o //
NK100(the)011:222: 'o na des chog gam zhe na mi chog /shes pa ma nyams pa gcig dgos te /
NK100(the)011:223: de'i zlog pa bcad de nyams pa gang zhe na /
NK100(the)011:224: rlung dang lha 'dres dbang byas te shes pa rang bzhin du mi gnas so //
NK100(the)011:225: de ci'i phyir nyams na shes pa rang la dbang ma thob ste /
NK100(the)011:226: blo bskol du mi btub pas so //
NK100(the)011:227: ma nyams pa gang zhe na shes pa la rang dbang thob pa'o //
NK100(the)011:228: ci'i phyir zhe na blo chos phyogs su bskool du btub pa'i phyir ro //
NK100(the)011:229: 'o na des chog gam zhe na /
NK100(the)011:230: mi chog ste las nyams pa gcig dgos /
NK100(the)011:231: de'i zlog pa bcad de las nyams pa gang zhe na /
NK100(the)011:232: sdig pa'i phyogs su mos shing gzhom pa'o //
NK100(the)011:233: de yang skye ba nas sdig las 'ba' zhig la dga' ba yin te /
NK100(the)011:234: de ci'i phyir nyams na mi lus thob nas rnam
NK100(the)011:235: smin gyi khur khur nas ngan song du 'gro bas
NK100(the)011:236: so // ma nyams pa ni dge ba'i phyogs su mos shing gus pa'o //
NK100(the)011:237: de ci'i phyir na las 'phros bzang pos yar la 'dren pa'i phyir ro //
NK100(the)011:238: 'o na des chog gam zhe na mi chog ste /
NK100(the)011:239: las kyi mtha' ma log pa gcig dgos so //
NK100(the)011:240: de'i zlog pa bcad de ma tha' log pa gang zhe na /
NK100(the)011:241: sngon la chos byas nas 'jug tu mi chos byed pa'o //
NK100(the)011:243: mthar ma phyin te chos kyis phan ma thogs pas so //
NK100(the)011:244: ma log pa ni chos bzhin byas te chos mthar phyir pa'o //
NK100(the)011:245: 'o na dal bas chog gam byas nas mi chog ste 'byor pa dang ldan dgos so //
NK100(the)011:247: 'byor pa ni snang ba ma logs pa bdun dang ldan pa ste /
NK100(the)011:249: bde bar gshegs pa lung gi ma log pa ni /
NK100(the)011:250: bde bar gshegs pa'i lung snang ste /
NK100(the)011:251: bka' lung la lta ba dang 'bri ba dang /
NK100(the)011:252: klog nyan 'chad sgom du yod pas te /
NK100(the)011:253: dper na rdur mo la ngar yod pa ces bya ste /
NK100(the)011:254: lcags nag ngar dang ldan pa lta bu'o //
NK100(the)011:255: 'o na des chog gam mi chog ste /
NK100(the)011:256: lcags nag yod kyang me rdo dgos pa bzhin du /
NK100(the)011:257: bla ma bka'i snang ba ma log pa ni /
NK100(the)011:258: de'i don ston pa'i bla ma mtshan nyid ldan pa ste /
NK100(the)011:259: dper na mkhregs rdol zur yod pa ces bya ste me rdo zur can lta bu'o //
NK100(the)011:260: 'o na des chog gam mi chog ste /
NK100(the)011:261: de gnyis 'dzom yang btsa' dag pa bzhin du /
NK100(the)011:262: rang shes rab kyi snang ba ma log pa ni /
NK100(the)011:263: go ru rung rtogs su rung pa ste /
NK100(the)011:264: dper na btsa' la slan ma zhugs pa lta bu'o //
NK100(the)011:265: des chog gam mi chog ste /
NK100(the)011:267: me rdo gsum so sor bzhag pas mi 'ong /
NK100(the)011:268: sa gcig tu 'tshog dgos pa bzhin /
NK100(the)011:269: 'tshams sbyor byed pa dus kyi snang ba ma log na ni /
NK100(the)011:272: shes rab gsum dus gcig la 'tshogs dgos te /
NK100(the)011:273: dper na rdzas gsum po snga phyi dus gcig gi bsdus pa lta bu'o //
NK100(the)011:274: des chog gam na cung mi chog ste /
NK100(the)011:275: gsum po snod du bzhag pas mi phan /
NK100(the)011:276: lag pa'i rtsol bas rdeb dgos pa bzhin du /
NK100(the)011:277: bya ba dang byed pa las kyi snang ba ma log pa ni /
NK100(the)011:278: nyams su len la dgos pa yin te /
NK100(the)011:279: chos byas kyi dgos pa btags la /
NK100(the)011:280: dbang po rab 'bring gi sgo nas nyams su blang ste /
NK100(the)011:281: khyim pa'i cha lugs sogs pa rgyas par gsungs te /
NK100(the)011:282: dper na 'tshogs pa'i rjes la skyes bu lag gi rtsol ba zhugs pa lta bu'o //
NK100(the)011:283: des chog gam mi chog ste /
NK100(the)011:284: me thon yang che bar bskyed pa la shing dgos pa bzhin du /
NK100(the)011:285: yo byad rgyu'i snang ba ma log pa ni de lnga ste bsgrang /
NK100(the)011:286: dkar po'i chos spyod thams cad kyi gzhi dad pa yin pas che ba /
NK100(the)011:287: dad pa yod kyang le lor ltus pas grogs brtson 'grus yin pas che ba /
NK100(the)011:288: brtson 'grus yod kyang chos ston pa la bla ma
NK100(the)011:289: gal che bas rkyen mtshan nyid dang ldan pa'i bla
NK100(the)011:290: ma / bla ma yod kyang gdams ngag nyams su len dgos pas /
NK100(the)011:292: sgom pa la yang bar chad byung na sangs mi rgyas bas /
NK100(the)011:293: lam bar chad med pa ste /
NK100(the)011:294: dper na shing gi bungs cher yod pa lta bu'o //
NK100(the)011:295: des chog gam byas pas mi chog ste /
NK100(the)011:296: de rnams 'tshogs nas la la bsregs la la 'tshed pa bzhin du /
NK100(the)011:297: mthar phyin pa 'bras bu'i snang ba ma log pa ni /
NK100(the)011:298: gong gi bka' lung la sogs pa de rnams kyis
NK100(the)011:299: nyon mongs rnam rtog la sogs rang rgyud pa 'di
NK100(the)011:301: rang bzhin ngo shes pas nus pa med par byas pa'o //
NK100(the)011:302: dper na bsreg 'tshed kyi bya ba byed pa'i mi lta bu'o //
NK100(the)011:303: dal ba ma nyams pa bdun /
NK100(the)011:304: 'byor pa rnam pa ma log pa bdun po de bshad pas /
NK100(the)011:305: dal 'byor nam dgos pa na thob snyam na /
NK100(the)011:306: dal 'byor de thob par dka' ba bstan te de la gsum /
NK100(the)011:307: thob par dka' ba'i gtan tshigs ma thob pa'i skyon /
NK100(the)011:310: dus rnam pa gsum du nyams log gnyis 'byung pa'i phyir /
NK100(the)011:311: dal 'byor phun sum 'tshogs pa de thob dka' bar brtag ces pas bstan te /
NK100(the)011:312: dus gsum ni 'das ma 'ongs da lta ba'o //
NK100(the)011:313: nyams log gnyis 'byung ba'i phyir ni /
NK100(the)011:314: rten nyams pa ngan song gsum gyi sems can rgya che zhing grangs mang ste /
NK100(the)011:315: rigs drug nang na dmyal ba tshan che /
NK100(the)011:316: de bas yi dwags stong 'gyur gyis nyung /
NK100(the)011:317: de la byings na gnas pa dang /
NK100(the)011:318: kha 'thor ba gnyis las kha 'thor pa nyung pa yin te /
NK100(the)011:319: kha 'thor ba la yang ri la gnas pa'i ri dwags dang gcan gzan /
NK100(the)011:321: sa 'og 'bu srin dang byi ba la sogs pa /
NK100(the)011:322: mis bdag tu bzung ba'i phyugs la sogs pa /
NK100(the)011:323: sems can gyi lus la gnas pa'i shig dang sro ma /
NK100(the)011:324: mi'i lus la nang na srin bu stong phrag brgyad cu /
NK100(the)011:325: de re re'i nang na srin tsi tsi gling kha'i grong khyer lnga brgya /
NK100(the)011:326: bar snang gi sbrang bu rngo phug gcig gi srog chags la yang zad pa med do //
NK100(the)011:327: de la ltos na rten ma nyams pa mi lus co lo las med do //
NK100(the)011:328: log pa'i dbang du byas na /
NK100(the)011:329: bde bar gshegs pa lung gi snang ba log pa ni /
NK100(the)011:330: mdo nas sangs rgyas kyi gsung mi drag pa mang du btud nas 'ong /
NK100(the)011:331: b+hu d+ha'i gsung drag pa sgron ma'i skal pa ni re re las mi 'ong par gsungs /
NK100(the)011:332: sgron ma'i skal pa la'ang bka' lung med par rgyal khams mang la /
NK100(the)011:333: ma log pa rgya gar ram bod yul dbus su
NK100(the)011:334: skyes pa las dang skal bar ldan pa lung la
NK100(the)011:335: spyod pa cal le las med do //
NK100(the)011:336: des na dal 'byor phun sum tshogs pa 'di shin tu thob par daka'o //
NK100(the)011:337: nyams pa gling chen po gsum dang gling phran brgyad /
NK100(the)011:338: ma nyams pa 'dzam bu'i gling gcig pu /
NK100(the)011:339: log pa'i skabs su bla ma dang ma mjal ba bsam gyis mi khyab /
NK100(the)011:340: mjal bcal le las med pas kyang daka'o //
NK100(the)011:341: gnas nyams pa byang kha sna brgyad dang /
NK100(the)011:342: mon dang kla klo dang 'bog chor gyi sde la sogs pa bsam gyis mi khyab /
NK100(the)011:343: ma nyams pa rgya gar rdo rje gdan dang /
NK100(the)011:344: bod yul dbus tsam las mi 'dug /log pa chos mi go ba ni mang /
NK100(the)011:345: go ba cal le las med pas kyang daka'o //
NK100(the)011:346: dbang po nyams pa 'on dig long ba la sogs pa'am /
NK100(the)011:347: de nyung kyang blo don gyi dbang po lnga nyams te /
NK100(the)011:348: dad pa'i dbang po nyams te chos la mi gus /
NK100(the)011:349: brtson 'grus kyi dbang po nyams te le lo che /
NK100(the)011:350: dran pa'i dbang po nyams te chos mi dran /
NK100(the)011:351: shes rab kyi dbang po nyams te mi go /
NK100(the)011:352: ting nge 'dzin gyi dbang po nyams te sems mi gnas pa mang la /
NK100(the)011:353: de las bzlog pa nyung bas so //
NK100(the)011:357: shes rab gsum dus gcig 'dzoms pa ni nyung /
NK100(the)011:358: ma 'dzom pa la mang pas kyang daka'o //
NK100(the)011:359: shes pa nyams shes pa la rang dbang ma thob ste chos la mi gus pa mang /
NK100(the)011:360: ma nyams te shes pa la rang dbang thob cing chos la gus pa ni nyung ba'o //
NK100(the)011:361: log pa'i skabs su chos nas gsungs pa bzhin byed pa ni nyung /
NK100(the)011:362: chos bzhin du mi byed pas kyang pas daka'o //
NK100(the)011:363: las nyams te sdig pa'i phyogs su mos pa ni mang /
NK100(the)011:364: ma nyams te dge ba la mos pa ni nyung pa'o //
NK100(the)011:365: log pa'i skabs su yo byad rgyu lnga ma 'dzom pa ni mang /
NK100(the)011:366: 'dzam pa ni cal le las med pas kyang daka'o //
NK100(the)011:367: las kyi mtha' log ste chos mthar ma phyin pa ni mang /
NK100(the)011:369: log pa'i skabs su 'bras bu mthar ma phyin pa
NK100(the)011:370: na mang 'bras bu mthar phyin pa cal le las
NK100(the)011:371: mi 'dug pa'i phyir dal 'byor phun 'tshogs pa de
NK100(the)011:372: shin tu thob par dka' bar brtag go //
NK100(the)011:373: 'o na de tsam thob par dka' ba de /
NK100(the)011:374: thob rung ma thob rung snyam na /
NK100(the)011:375: ma thob pa'i skyon la lnga ste /
NK100(the)011:377: 'bras bu sgrub pa'i thabs med pa'i skyon /
NK100(the)011:378: thabs de rang yod rung med rung snyam na /
NK100(the)011:379: 'bras bu ma thob na 'khor bar 'khyam pa'i skyon /
NK100(the)011:380: 'khor bar kyang 'khyam rung mi 'khyam rung snyam na /
NK100(the)011:381: 'khor bar 'khyams na nyes dmigs 'byung ba'i skyon no //
NK100(the)011:383: spyir 'khor ba'i nyes dmigs sdug bsngal yin /
NK100(the)011:384: sdug bsngal sdug bsngal bsam gyis mi khyab brjod kyis mi rdzogs kyang /
NK100(the)011:385: sh+ri sing ngas dgu ru bsdus nas bstan pa la /
NK100(the)011:387: 'tsho ba'i gnas la brtson ra lta bu'i nyes dmigs ni /
NK100(the)011:388: dper na mi gcig dga' yangs su yod pa la /
NK100(the)011:389: brtson du bzung pas sdug bsngal te /
NK100(the)011:390: rkang lag rdos su bcug pas yan lag brkyang bskum bya dbang med de lus sdug bsngal /
NK100(the)011:391: khong ci zer nyan gyi lcam bu gsol dgos te ngag sdug bsngal /
NK100(the)011:392: shi yis dogs rkang lag chad kyis dgos pas sems sdug bsngal /
NK100(the)011:393: ma shi yang nor dang 'bral snyam nas yid sdug bsngal bzhin du /
NK100(the)011:394: sems stong gsal gyi 'dug tshul de /
NK100(the)011:395: nyon mongs dug lnga'i dbang du song ste /
NK100(the)011:397: rigs drug gi gnas su bzung ste /
NK100(the)011:398: spyi dang bye brag gi sdug bsngal nyams su myong /
NK100(the)011:399: 'o na dug lnga de gang nas byung zhe na /
NK100(the)011:401: rgyud la skye ba'i nyon mongs lta bu'i nyes dmigs ni /
NK100(the)011:402: dper na rgyal mo rag na srin bu pa ta bya ba yod de /
NK100(the)011:404: sgo nga sbas nas nam zla gros pa dang /
NK100(the)011:405: bu mo gzhon nu'i drod la btsas pas srin du song /
NK100(the)011:406: de rdza mar bcug pas thar du re nas 'gul bas bal skye nas srog dang bral /
NK100(the)011:407: des cog gi bsdad na bal mi skye /
NK100(the)011:408: de ma skyes na mi 'chi ba la gdod ma shes pa bzhin du /
NK100(the)011:409: nyon mongs dug lnga po 'di yang /
NK100(the)011:412: shar lho nub byang nas ma byung /
NK100(the)011:413: rang gi rgyud las skyes te /
NK100(the)011:414: dbang po sgo lnga'i yul du yul lnga shar ba la /
NK100(the)011:416: mi sdug pa la zhe sdang /
NK100(the)011:417: gnyis med du ma shes na gti mug /rang las nga rgyal /
NK100(the)011:419: rang sems glod nas sdod shes na nyon mongs mi skye /
NK100(the)011:420: de ma skyes na rgyud mi 'ching 'khor bar mi 'khyam pa yin pa la /
NK100(the)011:421: sdod ma shes rgyud bcings shing 'khor bar 'khyams pa'o //
NK100(the)011:422: sdig pa'i las la spyad pa la brtson dug la spyod pa lta bu ni /
NK100(the)011:423: dper na btsan dug ro mngar ba myangs pas zhim snyam nas zos pas /
NK100(the)011:424: der kho'i nus pas mchu dang lce los pa thams cad gas nas /
NK100(the)011:425: lus na tshas gang tha ma srog dang bral ba bzhin du /
NK100(the)011:426: srog gcod pa dang ma byin pa len par la sogs pa byas pas /
NK100(the)011:427: lto rgyab la 'phral la phan pa snyam byed kyang /
NK100(the)011:428: tshe 'di rang la yang phan pa che mi thogs /
NK100(the)011:429: tha ma de'i nus pas ngan song gi sdug bsngal nyams su myong pa'o //
NK100(the)011:430: rnyed pa dang bkur bsti la gnyi dang rgya lta bu ni /
NK100(the)011:431: rnyed pa la gnyis lta bu ste /
NK100(the)011:432: dper na bya rgod snyam na /
NK100(the)011:433: gzan ma btsal la rang yang bza' /
NK100(the)011:434: phru gu yang gso snyam nas gzan la phyin pas /
NK100(the)011:435: gnyi la zin te rang yang bzar med /
NK100(the)011:436: phru gu la yang 'khyer du med par tha ma srog dang bral ba bzhin du /
NK100(the)011:437: mi 'ong gnyis bsdebs nas bu tsha blags nas /
NK100(the)011:438: rnyed pa btsal la bu tsha yang gso /
NK100(the)011:439: rang yang bza' snyam tsa na /
NK100(the)011:440: nad dam dgra la sogs pas phog nas /
NK100(the)011:442: bu tsha la sbyin du yang med /
NK100(the)011:443: srog dang bral tha ma 'dod pa de then thag byas nas ngan song du lhung pa'o //
NK100(the)011:444: bskur bsti la rgya lta bu ni /
NK100(the)011:445: dper na ri dwags rnams rtsa bzang sar phyin la /
NK100(the)011:446: rang la bskur bya snyam tsa na /
NK100(the)011:447: lam du rgya la zin nas /
NK100(the)011:448: rtsa bza' dbang med par 'chi ba bzhin du /
NK100(the)011:449: pho reng mo reng mo red du yod tsam na gza' mi bsdebs na skyid pa /
NK100(the)011:450: gcig 'ong snyam nas gnyis bsdebs pas /
NK100(the)011:451: bu tsha je mang je mang song /
NK100(the)011:452: ka cha je chung je nyung song nas skyid du
NK100(the)011:453: re tsam na tha rgyug pa zing nge sprang dgos
NK100(the)011:454: so // tha ma yang des ngan song du then theg byed do //
NK100(the)011:455: ngag don dril ni gnyi dang rgya la zin pa mi thar ba bzhin du /
NK100(the)011:456: rnyed pa dang bkur bsti la chags nas 'khor ba las mi thar ro //
NK100(the)011:457: sdang ba'i dgra la nad gdug pa can nam rims mi zad pa lta bu ni /
NK100(the)011:458: dpe nad gdug pa can mdze ni dang po nas phyur gyis mi 'ong ste /
NK100(the)011:459: steng gdon snying la zhugs pas snying mi dga' /
NK100(the)011:460: de nas 'og gdon lus la zhugs pas sha 'phrig dang /
NK100(the)011:461: drang thig dang cha 'brab la sogs pa 'ong /
NK100(the)011:462: tha ma lam nas de las mi thar pa dang /
NK100(the)011:463: rims ma zad pa yang dang po nas yar sun gyis mi 'gro ste /
NK100(the)011:464: phrum ser dang tshigs bzhi na ba las so'o //
NK100(the)011:465: de nas yor khrud kyis tshud nas de las mi thar pa bzhin du /
NK100(the)011:466: dgra yang dang po kha tsam tshig tsam la mi
NK100(the)011:467: sha nor sha la sogs par song nas de las
NK100(the)011:468: mi thar ro // ngag don na madze'am rims nad
NK100(the)011:469: kyis zin pa de mi thar bar 'chi ba bzhin
NK100(the)011:470: mi thar ro // du / dgra la zhe sdang che bas de 'khor ba las mi thar ro //
NK100(the)011:471: gdung pa'i gnyen la 'khor ba'i shal thag lta bu ni /
NK100(the)011:472: dper na shal ba shal ba'i dus su /
NK100(the)011:473: thag pa ske la bskon pas gang du phyin yang 'ji yor re bong pa bzhin du /
NK100(the)011:474: gdung pa'i gnyen la zhen chags kyi thag pa ma chad pas /
NK100(the)011:475: gang du 'gro yang yid breng nge 'ong ste /
NK100(the)011:476: tha ma des ngan song du bsgyur ro //
NK100(the)011:477: zang zing gi nor la byur gyi rdos lta bu ni /
NK100(the)011:478: dper na rkang pa rdos su bcug pas spyod lam gang ltar byas kyang ma bde ba bzhin du /
NK100(the)011:479: nor la chags shing zhen nas de'i nyar byas pas /
NK100(the)011:480: de chud zos kyis dogs nas gang ltar byas kyang ma bade'o //
NK100(the)011:481: tha ma yang ngan song du bskyur ro //
NK100(the)011:482: mi lus la sgyu ma lta bu ni /
NK100(the)011:483: dper na sgyu ma snang la rang bzhin gyis stong ste bden par grub pa med pa bzhin du /
NK100(the)011:484: mi lus zag bcas kyi phung po 'di yang rten
NK100(the)011:485: 'brel 'tshogs pa las gnas skabs su grub pa ltar
NK100(the)011:486: snang yang bden pa'i rang bzhin gyis stong pa'o //
NK100(the)011:487: mi tshe la chu bur lta bu'i nyes dmigs ni /
NK100(the)011:488: dper na chu bur rkyen gyis 'bur tser skyes kyang /
NK100(the)011:490: blo gtad med pa bzhin du /
NK100(the)011:491: mi tshe 'di yang pha ma'i rgyu rkyen gyi na gcig las grub /
NK100(the)011:492: da lta yang bden pa ltar snang yang snying po
NK100(the)011:493: dang blo gtad med de nam 'chi cha med do
NK100(the)011:494: // de rnams thos pa la brten nas mi bzung /
NK100(the)011:495: de la brten nas bsam mno btang ste /
NK100(the)011:496: nyes dmigs de rnams nges par 'dug pas zhen pa log gis 'gro dgos pa yin no //
NK100(the)011:497: de skad byas pas nyes dmigs byung tsam na 'khor ba gzhag pas chog snyam na /
NK100(the)011:498: gzhag dka' ba'i skyon la dgu ste bsgrang /
NK100(the)011:500: la la'i snang ba dgras brid /
NK100(the)011:501: dgra btul la chos bya snyam /
NK100(the)011:506: la la bshes gnyen gyis snang ba brid nas chos ma grub pa'o //
NK100(the)011:507: rig pa col chung ba ni /
NK100(the)011:508: rig pa col che na snang ba 'brid mkhas kyi rjes su mi 'brang pa la /
NK100(the)011:509: rjes su 'brangs pas rig pa col chung ngo //
NK100(the)011:510: ma btags pa'i 'khor ba nyams dga' ni /
NK100(the)011:511: brtags shing dpyad na 'khor ba sdug bsngal gyi rtsa ba skyug bro ba yin pa la /
NK100(the)011:512: ma brtags pas bu mang na dga' /
NK100(the)011:513: nor che na dga' ba la sogs pa'o //
NK100(the)011:515: dang po kha smras 'di bsal la /
NK100(the)011:516: sang phod skyid pa cig bya snyam tsa na /
NK100(the)011:517: sdug bsngal chu'i gnyer ma dang 'dra ste /
NK100(the)011:519: sdug bsngal lu gu rgyud gcig gsham la gcig sbrel nas 'ong /
NK100(the)011:521: rba tsha sa ma da ltar skyid par yod kyang /
NK100(the)011:522: shi chad dang god 'gram la sogs pa byung nas sdug bsngal du 'gyur ro //
NK100(the)011:523: nyon mongs pa dbang che ni /
NK100(the)011:524: chos bya snyam tsa na nyon mongs pa'i rkyen dang
NK100(the)011:525: phrad pas chos kyis mi zlog par rang dbang med
NK100(the)011:528: 'dod pa'i yon tan la sogs pa la 'dzin sems
NK100(the)011:529: kyis rang kri mar 'dzin pa de las thar bar
NK100(the)011:530: daka'o // zhen chags kha drag ste /
NK100(the)011:531: nor rdzas la zhen cing chags te tha na ming gi yang zhen pa ma grol lo //
NK100(the)011:532: ma brtags pa'i rgya mtsho gting ring ba ni /

NK100(the)011:534: rtogs pa snyam byed kyang ma rtogs te /

NK100(the)011:538: lus bsam gyis mi khyab pa blangs /
NK100(the)011:539: las bsam gyis mi khyab pa bsags pas /
NK100(the)011:540: las kyi 'khor lo ri gzar gyi chu dang 'dra bas ded nas chos byar mi khom pa'o //
NK100(the)011:541: de yang thos pa la brten nas mi bzung /
NK100(the)011:542: de'i don bsams gzhag dka' yang gzhag dgos pa yin no //
