NK100(the)011:621: dad pa med na byang chub kyi myu gu mi
NK100(the)011:622: smin pa bzhin du thar pa'i 'bras bu mi 'byung
NK100(the)011:623: ngo // de ltar med na skyon 'dug pas bzhag pas mi phan pas 'tshol dgos pas /
NK100(the)011:625: rgyud bzhi la brten te dad pa brtsal ba ni /
NK100(the)011:627: de'i dang po bla ma'i rgyud la brten te dad pa brtsal ba la gnyis las dang po /
NK100(the)011:628: mdza' spyod la brten te dad pa brtsal ba ni /
NK100(the)011:629: bla ma mtshan nyid dang ldan pa /
NK100(the)011:631: phyi ma 'ba' zhig don du gnyer ba /
NK100(the)011:632: ci mdzad chos dang bstun pa /
NK100(the)011:633: 'og gi mtshan nyid bcu gnyis dang mthun pa'i mdzad
NK100(the)011:634: spyod kyi yon tan mthong pas dad pa rnyed do
NK100(the)011:635: // gdams ngag las brtsal ba ni /
NK100(the)011:636: gdams ngag zab mo zhus de ma gred par nan chags byas pas dad pa rnyed do //
NK100(the)011:638: drang don la brten te dad pa btsal ba ni /
NK100(the)011:639: drang don gyi mdo bltas pas khyim bdag dpal skyes sam /
NK100(the)011:640: dbul mo gnyen dga' mos mar me skya gcig phul bas kyang 'bras bu thob pa la sogs pa'am /
NK100(the)011:641: sdig pa'i rnam par smin pas ngan song la sogs
NK100(the)011:642: pa'i sdug bsngal 'byung bar gsungs pas dad pa rnyed
NK100(the)011:644: 'jig rten yongs kyi spyod yul la /
NK100(the)011:645: sangs rgyas gsung gi zab mo 'byung la sogs pa'i lung zab mo la brten nas /
NK100(the)011:646: da ltar 'khor ba'i sdug bsngal gyi snang ba 'di
NK100(the)011:647: chos nyid du ngo sprad pas nges shes nang nas
NK100(the)011:648: skyes te dad pa rnyed do //
NK100(the)011:651: gong du bstan pa'i dal 'byor de thob dka' ba la /
NK100(the)011:652: de thob kyi gting la lam sna 'dzin dgos /
NK100(the)011:653: da res dal 'byor thob pa la ma zin na
NK100(the)011:654: gtan du 'khor bar 'khyams par 'dug snyam pas rnyed
NK100(the)011:655: do // mi rtag pa rgyud la bskyed pa ni /
NK100(the)011:657: 'chi nges sngar lus pa'i sems can mi 'dug /de
NK100(the)011:658: yang nam mchi cha med tshe la nges pa mi
NK100(the)011:659: 'dug / 'chi bdag gi bdud kyis bzung 'chi nad drag pos btab pa'i dus su /
NK100(the)011:660: yul dang khang khyim bzang yang mi phan thon nas 'gro dgos /
NK100(the)011:661: nye 'brel bzang yang ma phan bral nas 'gro dgos /
NK100(the)011:662: nor rdzas che yang ma phan bzhag nas 'gro dgos te /
NK100(the)011:663: chos med ces kyang mi phan par 'dug snyam pa rgyud la skye nas rnyed do //
NK100(the)011:665: bde ba la brten nas brtsal ba ni /
NK100(the)011:666: gzhan bde zhing skyid pa ni bsod nams bsags pa las byung ste /
NK100(the)011:667: bdag kyang mi dge ba rgyab tu skyur /
NK100(the)011:668: 'di phyi gnyis kar bde snyam pa rnyed do //
NK100(the)011:669: sdug bsngal ni gzhan sdug cing bsngal ba 'di rnams ni sdig pa'i rnam smin yin pas /
NK100(the)011:670: 'jigs shing skyo nas sdig pa spangs /
NK100(the)011:671: dge ba dang du blangs pas rnyed do //
NK100(the)011:672: de ltar btsal bas rnyed na dad pa yod pa'i yon tan ci yod na /
NK100(the)011:673: yon tan yod pa yon tan gyi dpe drug ni bsgrags dang pa yod pa'i gang zag ni /
NK100(the)011:674: dper na zhing sa bshin pa dang 'dra ste /
NK100(the)011:675: dper na zhing sa bshin pa gcig la /
NK100(the)011:676: 'bru gang btab kyang char thon la sogs pa'i rkyen gyis ma gnod pa 'bras bu smin pa bzhin /
NK100(the)011:677: dad pa yod pa theg pa gang la zhugs kyang /
NK100(the)011:678: nyon mongs la sogs pa'i rkyen gyis ma gnod de 'bras bu thob bo //
NK100(the)011:679: chu bo sgrol ba'i gru ni /
NK100(the)011:680: dper na chu pha kar grus sgrol ba bzhin /
NK100(the)011:681: 'khor ba'i chu bo las dad pa'i grus sgrol nas byang chub kyi skam sar phyin no //
NK100(the)011:682: 'jigs pa chen po'i skyal ma ni /
NK100(the)011:683: dper na 'jigs sar 'gro ba skyel ma bzang po cig yod na /
NK100(the)011:684: dgras kha ngan cig kyang gtang mi nus pa bzhin du /
NK100(the)011:685: 'khor ba'i 'jigs pa la dad pa'i skyel ma yod
NK100(the)011:686: pas 'khor bar bkyigs grags nas bskyur kyang mi 'agro'o
NK100(the)011:688: dper na tshong dpon gyis dbus gtsang gdabs nas dgos
NK100(the)011:689: pa'i zong btsongs nas bdag gzhan gyis don phun sum
NK100(the)011:691: dad pa yod pas rang yang bla na med pa'i byang chub kyi 'bras bu thob /
NK100(the)011:693: yang na tshong dpon gyis lam sna khrid pas nyes pa med par tshong log pa bzhin du /
NK100(the)011:694: dad pas lam sna khrid pas bar chad med par 'bras bu thob pa'o //
NK100(the)011:696: dper na so 'tshams mkhar bzang po cig yod na /
NK100(the)011:697: dgra'i 'jigs pas mi tshugs pa bzhin du /
NK100(the)011:698: 'khor 'das kyi so 'tshams nas dad pa yod pas
NK100(the)011:699: 'khor ba'i 'jigs pa dang nyon mongs kyi gnod pas
NK100(the)011:700: ma tshugs so // yid bzhin gyi nor bu rin po che ni /
NK100(the)011:701: dper na nor bu phyi bas phyis /
NK100(the)011:703: rgyal mtshan gyi rtse mo btags nas mchod pas dgos 'dod thams cad 'byung ba bzhin du /
NK100(the)011:704: dad pa la brten nas dgos 'dod nyams su blangs nas /
NK100(the)011:705: tshe 'di'i dgos 'dod lam gyi drod rtags dang mngon shes la sogs pa yang 'byung /
NK100(the)011:706: mthar thams cad mkhyen pa'i sangs rgyas kyang thob bo //
NK100(the)011:707: de ltar yon tan yod pa'i dad pa de /
NK100(the)011:708: rang la yang mi 'dug brtsal bas yang ma rnyed na /
NK100(the)011:709: bsgrang pa'i mtshang gi dpe drug ni drug ste bsgrang /
NK100(the)011:710: srog ma chad pa'i ro yin pa ni /
NK100(the)011:711: srog breng breng 'di ma chad kyang dad pa med pas ro yin gshin gyi khongs su gdab /
NK100(the)011:712: chang ma 'thungs kyang chos ma dran pas ro yin pa ni /
NK100(the)011:713: lha 'dres ma bslabs kyang dad pa med pas lus ngag gi spyod pa 'chal te bsnyon pa /
NK100(the)011:714: dad pa med na zug bzhi sa la mi 'dzugs kyang byol song gi khongs su gdab /
NK100(the)011:715: skyas pa ji ltar yon tan dang ldan zho sha
NK100(the)011:716: dang gros mdun mkhas pa la sogs pa yon tan
NK100(the)011:717: kyang glang gser gyi rnal chu can yin dad pa
NK100(the)011:718: med pas glang / tshe 'di'i yon tan dang ldan pas gser gyi rnal chu'o //
NK100(the)011:719: bud med 'dzangs pa dang mtshar ba la sogs pa'i
NK100(the)011:720: yon tan ci yod kyang ba g.yu'i khol thag can
NK100(the)011:721: yin / dad pa med pas ba /
NK100(the)011:722: tshe 'di'i yon tan g.yu'i khol thag go //
NK100(the)011:723: de ltar med pa la skyon 'dug yod pa la
NK100(the)011:724: yon tan 'dug /gti pa med na bsgrang pa'i mtshang
NK100(the)011:725: 'dug pas rgyud la brten dgos so //
NK100(the)011:727: rgyun la brten pa'i thabs drug ni bsgrang /
NK100(the)011:728: spyir bzhi tshan drug las dad pa skye ba'i yul bzhi ni /
NK100(the)011:729: mos pa'i dad pa sangs rgyas chos dang /
NK100(the)011:730: bla ma gsum la brten nas ni /
NK100(the)011:731: sangs rgyas kyis sku la brten nas skye ni /
NK100(the)011:732: dper na jo bo sh+aakya lta bu ma mthong tsa na mos rgyu med kyang /
NK100(the)011:733: mthong pas phyag 'tshal bskor ba byed pa la sogs te /
NK100(the)011:735: chos kyi gsung la brten nas skye ba ni /
NK100(the)011:736: ma thos tsam na mi mos pa thos nas mos pa'o //
NK100(the)011:737: bla ma'i thugs la brten nas skye ste /
NK100(the)011:739: byin rlabs zhugs nas mos pa'o //
NK100(the)011:740: dang pa'i dad pa nyon mongs pa dug lnga chos nyid du shes pa la brten nas skye ni /
NK100(the)011:741: dang po dug lnga ngos bzung ste /
NK100(the)011:742: zhe sdang me ltar du 'bar te yul rkyen ngan pa dang phrad tsam na tsig rum pa de'o //
NK100(the)011:743: 'dod chags tsha la dang gar spyin bzhin du 'thas te /
NK100(the)011:744: phyi 'dod pa'i yon tan lnga la chags pa dang /
NK100(the)011:745: nang sems can 'khrigs pa la chags pa'o //
NK100(the)011:747: chos spyi dang rang gi mtshan nyid ma shes pa'o //
NK100(the)011:748: nga rgyal ri ltar gdos te /
NK100(the)011:751: gzhan gyi yon tan phrag dog tu mi shong ste nyes na dga' ba'o //
NK100(the)011:752: yang zhe sdang snam pa gsal /
NK100(the)011:756: shes bzhin du mi spyod pa gti mug go //
NK100(the)011:758: zhe sdang lta bu kam tser skyes tsa na de la kha nang du log nas bltas pas /
NK100(the)011:759: zhe sdang la ngo bo grub pa mi 'dug pa stong pa'i chos nyid /
NK100(the)011:760: de ltar shar ba de 'dzin med kyi rig pa zhe sdang du shar ba snang ba'i chos nyid /
NK100(the)011:761: de gnyis su mdo dang 'dzin med kyi rig pa /
NK100(the)011:763: de ltar shar rdo tsam na ngo bo grub pa med de /
NK100(the)011:764: ngos bzung dang bral bas ngo sprad pas /
NK100(the)011:765: tha ma zhe sdang snang stong gnyis med kyi ngang du rang grol lo //
NK100(the)011:766: de ltar nyon mongs zhe sdang gi steng nas gsal stong gnyis med kyi lta sgom gcig skye'o //
NK100(the)011:767: des dug lnga dang rtog pa kun 'agro'o //
NK100(the)011:768: de ltar dug lnga chos nyid shes pas dang pa gsum skye ste /
NK100(the)011:769: gdams ngag 'di 'bru ston pa'i bla ma bka' drin che snyam ste bla ma la dang /
NK100(the)011:770: nga rang yang dga' mor 'dug dug lnga rang grol snyam nas rang la dang /
NK100(the)011:771: bla ma dang chos ni cig nga la yod pa
NK100(the)011:772: bzhin khong la yang yod re dga' snyam mched grogs
NK100(the)011:773: la dang ba'o // yid ches pa'i dad pa las rgyu 'bras la brten nas skye ba ni /
NK100(the)011:774: dge bas 'bras bu bde legs sam mtho ris /
NK100(the)011:775: sdig pas 'bras bu ngan song ngam sdug bsngal de ltar yid ches pa'o //
NK100(the)011:777: mthar phyin pa'i dad pa skye ba'i yul ni /
NK100(the)011:778: dad pa de rnams rang gi rgyud pa la tshang zhing rdzogs pa la brten nas skye na /
NK100(the)011:779: gong ma de rnams rdzogs pas mthar phyin pa'o //
NK100(the)011:780: de ltar dad pa skyes pa de spel dgos pas /
NK100(the)011:782: bla ma dam pa'i spun du brten cing mos gus kyi gdung pa tshud nas 'phel ni /
NK100(the)011:783: bla ma ci byed chos dang bstun pa mtshan nyid
NK100(the)011:784: dang ldan pa la mos gus tshud na dad pa
NK100(the)011:785: 'phel / 'gyur ba yin pas ma tshud na 'grib /
NK100(the)011:787: grogs khyad par can gyi mdzad spyod la brten nas dad pa 'phel ba ni /
NK100(the)011:788: chos grogs khyad par can chos bzhin du byed pa brtson 'grus can dang 'grogs na dad pa 'phel /
NK100(the)011:789: bka' mdo lung zab mo la lta rtogs byas na dad pa 'phel ni /
NK100(the)011:790: bka' mdo dang lung drang don nges don la lta rtog byas na 'phel /
NK100(the)011:793: nam 'chi cha med 'chi ba la cis kyang mi
NK100(the)011:794: stongs snyam pa rgyud la skyes na dad pa 'phel
NK100(the)011:795: lo // de ltar spel ba la /
NK100(the)011:796: 'grim pa'i rkyen bzhi'i khar mi gtang ba ni /
NK100(the)011:798: dang po bla ma'i mdzad spyod log na dad pa 'grib ni /
NK100(the)011:799: rang gi bla ma ni chos dang ldan par yod
NK100(the)011:800: pa la jo mo la sogs pa'i rkyen gyis spyod
NK100(the)011:802: chos pa spyi'i spyod pa lag na 'grib pa ni /
NK100(the)011:803: rab byung gi sde khrug /sngags pa'i mthu rgyas /
NK100(the)011:805: dgon pa'i phrag dog la sogs pas 'grib /
NK100(the)011:806: rang gi sbyor gyi rtsol ba zhan na 'grib pa ni /
NK100(the)011:807: le lo'i dbang du song pa yin te /
NK100(the)011:809: bsgoms pa'i nyams med na 'grib dge /
NK100(the)011:810: mi chos kyi bya ba'i thog tu bab na 'grib ni /
NK100(the)011:811: nye 'brel la sogs mi chos kyi gnyer bab nas dge sbyor bya ma khom na 'grib bo //
NK100(the)011:812: de'i khar mi gtang pa ni bla ma'i mdzad spyod
NK100(the)011:813: log nas 'tshams med lnga byed kyang bla ma dgongs
NK100(the)011:814: pa can yin / 'o skol gyi dgongs pa mi log snyam pa byas la /
NK100(the)011:815: rang mos gus ma logs par bya /
NK100(the)011:816: chos pa spyi'i spyi las lta bu men gtong pas /
NK100(the)011:817: de bor la nyams len bya'o //
NK100(the)011:818: de ltar byas pas 'grib pa'i rkyen bzhi'i khar mi 'agro'o //
NK100(the)011:819: de ltar dad pa yod bya khar kyang mi 'ong /
NK100(the)011:820: med bya khar kyang mi 'ong pas /
NK100(the)011:821: de la dad pa yod pa'i rtags bzhis gtan la dbab ste /
NK100(the)011:822: rang thos bsam gyi shes rab la 'bad rtsol gyi nan tan che zhing /
NK100(the)011:823: rang gi rgyud sbyang pa la nan tan chen dad pa yod pa'i rtags yin /
NK100(the)011:824: rgyu dang yi dam lha la zhen thag pa nas gdung pa che na dad pa yod pa'i rtags /
NK100(the)011:825: sdig pa 'phra mo ngo rkog med par 'dzem na yang rtags /
NK100(the)011:826: che ngo tshas kyang 'dzem gsung ngo //
NK100(the)011:827: dge ba phra mo nas nyams len byed na rtags /
NK100(the)011:828: che ba grags pa 'dod pas kyang byed gsung ngo //
NK100(the)011:829: de ltar dad pa des ci byed na /
NK100(the)011:831: dge sbyor gyi rten byed pa ni /
NK100(the)011:832: dad pa la brten nas mdo 'don phyag 'tshal /
NK100(the)011:833: thos bsam sgom gsum la sogs pa byed do //
NK100(the)011:835: dad pa yod pas dge sbyor le lor mi 'jog ste nyams len sri li li byed pa'o //
NK100(the)011:836: man ngag thams cad kyi snod ni /
NK100(the)011:837: dad pa brten yod pas man ngag zhus nas nyams su len pa'o //
NK100(the)011:838: shes rab thams cad kyi 'dzin ni /
NK100(the)011:839: dad pa brtan pos nan tan byas pas khad nas chos go zhing zin nas 'ong ba'o //
NK100(the)011:840: de ltar dad pa de dpes mtshon na /
NK100(the)011:842: mos pa'i dad pa bu ma phyi na 'brel pa ni /
NK100(the)011:843: dper na bu lo gnyis gsum lon pa ni a
NK100(the)011:844: ma'i phyir 'breng ba la skyo ngas med pa bzhin
NK100(the)011:845: du / ru dang chos la mos te rjes su 'breng pa la skyo ngas med pa'o //
NK100(the)011:846: dang pa'i dad pa nor bu chu dwangs chu'i rnyog ma sel ba ni /
NK100(the)011:847: dper na nor bu chu dwangs phyar ba chu'i rnyog ma rang dwangs gzhin du /
NK100(the)011:848: sbyin pa la dang skyes pas ser sna rang dwangs su byed de /
NK100(the)011:850: yid ches pa'i dad pas rdo'i nang nas rin po
NK100(the)011:851: che rnyed pa ni dper na sa rdo'i nang nas
NK100(the)011:853: gzhan bas lhag par yid ches dga' zhing tshags byed pa bzhin du /
NK100(the)011:854: ru dang chos la lhag pa yid ches nas de'i rjes su 'jug cing dga' zhing spro'o //
NK100(the)011:855: mthar phyin pa'i dad pa rin po che'i nang nas
NK100(the)011:856: gser sa le sbram dang g.yu spu ris can 'chang
NK100(the)011:857: ba ni / dper na rin po che'i nang nas
NK100(the)011:858: gser sa le sbram dang g.yu spu ris ma rnyed
NK100(the)011:859: ba ni / pa ni / gtor gyis dogs nas mi 'brel bar 'chang ba bzhin du /
NK100(the)011:860: gong ma gsum po mthar phyin pas 'bras bu mi 'bral lags 'changs ma'o //
NK100(the)011:861: de ltar rgyud la brten pa la dad pa'i gol sa dgag pa la drug ste bsgrang /
NK100(the)011:862: de la bor ba la gnyis te bsgrang /
NK100(the)011:864: dang po dad pa'i stobs kyis dge sbyor dum gcig
NK100(the)011:865: byas pas des tshim nas phyir byar yod kyang mi
NK100(the)011:866: bya ba'o // gol sar bor ba ni /
NK100(the)011:867: dge sbyor cig bya bar 'dod pa la rkyen ngan cig dang phrad de sdig pa'i khar 'khyogs pa'o //
NK100(the)011:869: dang po dad pa yod dus su le los dge sbyor ma byas par /
NK100(the)011:870: des dred nas dad pa gtings skyer ma btub pa'o //
NK100(the)011:872: gzhon dus su dad pa du ma gcig yod pa la /
NK100(the)011:873: rgas kyi dad pa je chung je chung song pa'o //
NK100(the)011:875: dad pa'i dbang gis dge sbyor byas pa la /
NK100(the)011:876: ngas dge sbyor byas ngas thos pa byas /
NK100(the)011:877: ngas chos shes so snyam nas nga rgyal gyi dbang gis sems 'khegs pa'o //
NK100(the)011:878: byer ba ni dge sbyor byas ni ma byas bya'am mi bya snyam pa'i blo tshab tshub de'o //
NK100(the)011:879: zug pa ni dge sbyor ngos zung dam bcas pa
NK100(the)011:880: de ma grub na gzhan med byed par 'jog pa'o
NK100(the)011:881: // gol sa de rnams dgag pa na /
NK100(the)011:882: rang sar bor la de las bzlog ste /
NK100(the)011:883: dge sbyor dum cig byas pas mi phan ma shi'i bar du bya dgos so //
NK100(the)011:885: 'chi ba la cis kyang mi phan dge sbyor bya dgos so //
NK100(the)011:886: lag pa le lo'i dbang du mi btang bar brtson 'grus bskyed do //
NK100(the)011:887: zhu ba ni 'phel ba'i rgyu bzhis spel /
NK100(the)011:888: 'khyags pa la chos nyon mongs pa'i gnyen po yin pas dul bar bya'o //
NK100(the)011:889: byer ba la gang grub grub lag tu blangs la bya'o //
NK100(the)011:890: zug pa la phyogs ris med par gang grub bya'o //
NK100(the)011:891: de ltar byas pas gol sa khegs pa'o //
NK100(the)011:892: de ltar dad pa de rnams thos pa'i sgo nas ming bzung /
NK100(the)011:893: rgyud la tshang ma tshang blta /
NK100(the)011:894: ma tshang na skyon 'dug pas bsal /
NK100(the)011:895: yod pa la yon tan 'dug /btsal bas ma rnyed na bsgrang pa'i mtshang 'dug pas /
NK100(the)011:897: de la gol sa yod pas gol sa bkag la rgyud la gdab bo //
NK100(the)011:898: dad pa btsal ba'i le'u ste gnyis pa'o ////de ltar dad pa yod kyang /
NK100(the)011:899: dad pa can lam sna 'dren par byed la bla ma dgos pas /
NK100(the)011:900: bla ma brten pa la brgyad de bsgrang /
NK100(the)011:901: dang po dgos pa sgo gsum gyi sgo nas bla ma dam pa cig brten dgos pa ni /
NK100(the)011:902: byang chub kyi 'bras bu mi sgrub na bla ma brten kha na med /
NK100(the)011:903: sgrub na sgrub pa'i thabs lta sgom spyod pa la
NK100(the)011:904: sogs pa'i gros yul mi rgan po dang grong mi
NK100(the)011:905: khyim tshes la sogs pa la mi 'ong pas /
NK100(the)011:906: blo gros dri yul bla ma la brten dgos so //
NK100(the)011:907: bar du shes rab 'phel bar byed pa'i rkyen bla ma ni /
NK100(the)011:908: bla ma la brten pas dang po thos pa'i shes rab 'phel /
NK100(the)011:909: thos pa'i don bsams pas bsam pa'i shes rab 'phel /
NK100(the)011:910: de'i don la bsgom pas sgom pa'i shes rab 'phel
NK100(the)011:911: bar byed pa'i rkyen bla ma yin pas yin par
NK100(the)011:912: brten no // tha ma gang du 'gro ba shes rab par mdzad mkhan ni /
NK100(the)011:913: las mi dge bas ngan song /
NK100(the)011:915: de'i steng du snyan par smra zhing khrom mi bya la sogs pas lha /
NK100(the)011:916: lta sgom nyams su blangs na sangs rgyas pa la sogs pa bla mas shes pas brten no //
NK100(the)011:917: de ltar bla ma de gang rung rung la bya 'am snyam na /
NK100(the)011:918: des mi phan mtshan nyid dang ldan pa dgos pas /
NK100(the)011:919: mtshan nyid brtag pa la gnyis las /
NK100(the)011:920: thun mong gi bla ma mtshan nyid drug ni bsgrang /
NK100(the)011:921: dang po khungs nas byung ba'i lung dang ldan pa ni /
NK100(the)011:922: thug par thug pa'i chos 'chang ba ste /
NK100(the)011:923: de yang byin brlabs kyi rgyud pa rgyun ma chad
NK100(the)011:924: pa dbang gi chu bo ma nyams pa sogs pa'o
NK100(the)011:925: // thos bsam gyi shes rab la rgyud 'byongs pa ni /
NK100(the)011:927: bsam pas nang gi sgro 'dogs chod pa'o //
NK100(the)011:928: gtan la phebs pa'i rig pa khong du shar ba ni /
NK100(the)011:929: chos nyid ji ltar ba bzhin du rtogs pa'o //
NK100(the)011:930: phyin ci ma log pa'i gdams ngag ston shes pa ni /
NK100(the)011:931: rang la rtogs pa bzhin gzhan la'o //
NK100(the)011:932: 'gro ba'i don la brtson pa ni /
NK100(the)011:933: le lor mi sdod pa grub tshad du byed pa'o //
NK100(the)011:934: thugs rje la dbri bsnan chung pa ni /
NK100(the)011:935: mthong sems ma yin te kun la snyoms pa'o //
NK100(the)011:936: gnyis pa thun mong ma yin pa'i bla ma mtshan nyid drug ldan ni bsgrang /
NK100(the)011:937: dang po rtogs pa'i lta ba khyad du mi gsod pa'i bla ma ni /
NK100(the)011:938: de lta rtogs pa'i dus men kyang mi zer /
NK100(the)011:939: rtogs mi dgos 'di ka ltar yin mi zer te /
NK100(the)011:940: dal 'byor thob pa 'di rtogs pa'i dus yin /
NK100(the)011:941: bla mas ngo sprod dgos gsung ngo //
NK100(the)011:942: nyams myong gi sgom pa yal bar mi dor ba ni /
NK100(the)011:943: rtogs pa'i don la dmigs med kyi ngang la yengs med du 'jog pa'o //
NK100(the)011:944: bya byed kyi spyod pa gzhung ma log pa ni /
NK100(the)011:946: mthar phyin pa'i 'bras bu mngon du snang ba ni /
NK100(the)011:947: phag sdod pa min te mngon sum ngo sprod pa'o //
NK100(the)011:948: 'jig rten 'di'i chags zhen chung pa ni /
NK100(the)011:949: dam pa chos kyi dgos chen yin pas chags zhen chung pa'o //
NK100(the)011:950: phyi ma 'ba' zhig don du gnyer ba ni /
NK100(the)011:952: rnyed pa don du mi gnyer bar byang chub sgrub pa'o //
NK100(the)011:953: de ltar mtshan nyid dang ldan pa'i bla ma brten pa la rdzas dgos pas /
NK100(the)011:954: rdzas bsags pa la gsum ste bsgrang /
NK100(the)011:955: dad pa skye 'bri med pa chu bo'i gzhung lta bu ni /
NK100(the)011:956: dad pa gsum po res che res chung men te skye 'brir med pa'o //
NK100(the)011:957: brtson 'grus la thang lhod med pa gzhung brdung pa'i rgyud lta bu ni /
NK100(the)011:958: thos bsam bsgom pa la sogs pa'i nyams len la brtson pa'o //
NK100(the)011:959: dam tshig la 'gyur ldog med pa gser sa le sbram lta bu ni /
NK100(the)011:960: dper na gser sa le sbram la bsregs dpyod bdar
NK100(the)011:961: ba la sogs pa byas pas mi 'gyur ba bzhin
NK100(the)011:962: du / bla ma'i bka' bskyon la sogs ci byung yang dam tshig las mi 'gyur ba'o //
NK100(the)011:963: de tsho ni dam pa'i rdzas yin slob bu la dgos so //
NK100(the)011:964: de ltar rdzas 'tshogs nas gces pa drug gi sgo nas bla ma btsal ba ni drug ste bsgrang /
NK100(the)011:965: dang po rgyus med pa'i lam pa lta bur gcer pa ni /
NK100(the)011:966: dper na rgya gar rdo rje gdan lta bur 'gro
NK100(the)011:967: ba yin pas bar chad dang 'khyags 'khyogs med par
NK100(the)011:969: byang chub kyi lam la bar chad dang 'khyog med par 'khrid pa bla ma yin pas /
NK100(the)011:971: 'tshol ba'i tshul du bla ma btsal lo //
NK100(the)011:972: mi sha'o skyel ma lta bu gces ni /
NK100(the)011:973: dper mi sha'o dgra yul du 'gro ba la skyel ba bzang po dgos bzhin du /
NK100(the)011:974: 'khor ba las skyobs pa'i skye ba bla ma btsal lo //
NK100(the)011:975: mtshon cha skyob pa'i go cha lta bur gces pa ni /
NK100(the)011:976: dper na go cha bzang po yod na mtshon gyis mi phig bzhin du /
NK100(the)011:977: bla ma bzang po bsten nas nyon mongs kyi mtshon gyis mi phig pas /
NK100(the)011:978: khrug mgo 'tshol ba'i tshul du btsal lo //
NK100(the)011:979: nad gso ba'i sman lta bur gces pa ni /
NK100(the)011:980: dper na nad gso ba la sman pa gces pa ni sman pa 'tshol ba bzhin du /
NK100(the)011:981: khams gsum 'khor ba'ii nad gso bar byed pa'i sman pa bla ma btsal lo //
NK100(the)011:982: mun pa sel ba'i sgron me lta bur gces pa ni /
NK100(the)011:983: dper na mun pa sel ba sgron me gces pa bzhin /
NK100(the)011:984: ma rig pa'i mun pa sel ba'i sgron mer bla ma ces pa btsal lo //
NK100(the)011:985: dgos 'dod 'byung yid bzhin nor bu lta bur gces pa ni /
NK100(the)011:986: dper na rin po che la gsol ba 'debs na dgos 'dod 'byung ba de /
NK100(the)011:987: ded dpon gyis dka' las la brten nas tshol ba bzhin du /
NK100(the)011:988: bla ma la mchog thun mong gi dgos pa 'byung
NK100(the)011:989: ded dpon nor bu tshol ba'i tshul du bla ma
NK100(the)011:990: btsal lo // de ltar mtshan nyid dang ldan pa'i
NK100(the)011:991: bla ma de gces pa drug gi sgo nas btsal
NK100(the)011:993: bya ba srol lnga'i sgo nas brten pa ni lnga las bsgrang /
NK100(the)011:994: dang po theg pa che ba sa gzhi'i srol gyis bla ma bsten pa ni /
NK100(the)011:995: dper na sa gzhi la mi gtsang pa dang thab
NK100(the)011:996: dang gzhob la sogs pa ci byas kyang theg pa
NK100(the)011:997: bzhin du / bla mas kyang bka' bskyon pa la sogs pa ci byas bsten no //
NK100(the)011:998: drin len mi rtsib grub tshul dang brten pa ni /
NK100(the)011:999: dper na gru dgun chu grang mo dang dbyar chu
NK100(the)011:1000: chen ba la bsgral kyang drin mi rtsi ba bzhin
NK100(the)011:1001: du / lus ngag yid gsum dang zang zing gi
NK100(the)011:1002: zhabs thog ci byas kyang bla ma la drin mi
NK100(the)011:1005: 'gro na skyel 'ong na bsu 'jug ma 'dris zhing dga' ba bzhin du /
NK100(the)011:1006: bla ma la skyes su byed pa la sogs pa'o //
NK100(the)011:1007: mos pa ma phyin bu 'brel pa ni /
NK100(the)011:1008: dper na ma phyir bu 'breng pa la skyo ngas med pa bzhin du /
NK100(the)011:1009: bla ma'i phyir 'breng pa la skyo ngas med pa'o //
NK100(the)011:1010: gnyan po rgyal po gdan la bzhugs pa ni /
NK100(the)011:1011: dper na sa bdag rgyal po gdan la bzhugs pa'i
NK100(the)011:1012: tsar bag 'khums te ngan spyod byed mi nus pa
NK100(the)011:1013: bzhin du / bla ma'i spyan sngar bag med kyi spyod pa mi byed pa'o //
NK100(the)011:1014: de ltar brten nas bsnyen bskur ba ni /
NK100(the)011:1015: dang po sgo gsum dang pa'i bsnyen bskur bya ba ni /
NK100(the)011:1016: lus kyi sgo nas lha phyag dang bskor ba rgyun mi bcad /
NK100(the)011:1017: ngag gi sgo nas zhe sa dang ba stod ra rgyun mi bcad /
NK100(the)011:1018: de la bstod na sgra ni yon tan dang mthun par gtang /
NK100(the)011:1019: bstod grags pa sman sgrar song pa yang 'ong gsung /
NK100(the)011:1020: yid kyi sgo nas brtse ba dang gdung ba rgyun mi bcad par bya'o //
NK100(the)011:1021: ma chags pa'i bsnyen bskur bya ba ni /
NK100(the)011:1022: dang po dgos pa'i dam pa rang gi zhing khams yang ma chags par bla ma la dbul lo //
NK100(the)011:1023: gnyis pa gces pa'i dam pa rang gi bu smad kyang bzhes na bla ma la dbul te /
NK100(the)011:1024: rgyal sras dang ni rang gi lus //
NK100(the)011:1025: bu dang chung ma nor gyi dbyig /rab tu gces dang yid 'thad dbul //
NK100(the)011:1027: mi bzhed na zhabs 'dres yin pa mi dbul lo //
NK100(the)011:1028: gsum pa nor gyi dbyig dang /
NK100(the)011:1032: gos kyi kha dog la sogs pa ci bzhes pa bla ma la chags pa med par dbul lo //
NK100(the)011:1033: dgos pa ci yod na dgongs 'dus las /
NK100(the)011:1034: chos kun mi shes ma rtogs kyang //
NK100(the)011:1035: dam par gyur pa'i bla ma la //
NK100(the)011:1036: kun gnas rim gro cher byas na //
NK100(the)011:1038: ci phyir zhing rab gshin pa la //
NK100(the)011:1039: sa bon btab na rgyas 'phel bzhin //
NK100(the)011:1040: bsod nams dam pa'i zhing rab la //
NK100(the)011:1043: yang des ni na dang tsha ba dang /
NK100(the)011:1044: bkres dang skom pa'i sdug bsngal gyis /
NK100(the)011:1047: sgrub pa'i bsnyen bskur bya ba ni /
NK100(the)011:1048: rab lta thog nas sgrub nus pa ni /
NK100(the)011:1049: lta ba phyogs med rtogs pas yon tan phyogs zhen dang 'dzin pa grol te /
NK100(the)011:1050: de'i ngang la tshugs thub par sgrub bo //
NK100(the)011:1052: gsal stong ting nge 'dzin la nyams len re bya'o //
NK100(the)011:1053: tha ma spyod thog nas sgrub nus pa ni /
NK100(the)011:1054: g.yo med zag med kyis gzhi bzung la spyod pa chos dang ci mthun du bya'o //
NK100(the)011:1055: 'o na de bsnyen bskur du 'gro 'am zhe na /
NK100(the)011:1056: rang grol gzhan la phan thogs pa bsnyen bskur gyi mchog yin no //
NK100(the)011:1057: de ltar bsnyen bskur byas nas gdams ngag gi zhu tshul ni gnyis las /
NK100(the)011:1058: log par blta ba'i mthong lugs spangs la zhu ba ni /
NK100(the)011:1059: dang po rang rgyal por mthong pa ni /
NK100(the)011:1060: bla ma gsang che snyam pa'o //
NK100(the)011:1061: bla ma la tshang dpon ni /
NK100(the)011:1062: gdams ngag nor bu 'tshong par 'dug snyam pa'o //
NK100(the)011:1063: gdams ngag 'di bshad pa me tog dang yon blang snyom pa'o //
NK100(the)011:1064: grogs mtshungs par spyod pa la dgrar mthong ba ni /
NK100(the)011:1065: thos bsam sgom gsum mtshungs pa spyod pa'i grogs la /
NK100(the)011:1066: 'gran sems phrag dog gzhogs smod dang zur za gtong pa'o //
NK100(the)011:1067: nan tan gdams ngag go nas spyod pa ni tshe ma phyed du mthong pa ni /
NK100(the)011:1068: kha chos bzhin du byed pa la /
NK100(the)011:1073: tshe mthud kyi bu med zer ba la sogs pa'o //
NK100(the)011:1075: dug lnga nang du zhi dgra gdul mi dgos /
NK100(the)011:1076: 'brel med du shes pas gnyen gyi ngo mi bsrung /
NK100(the)011:1077: 'dod pa nang du zhi bas zas nor la dgos pa med /
NK100(the)011:1078: pha rtsabs bu rtsabs su gcod pa la tshe mthud kyi bu dgos pa med do //
NK100(the)011:1079: de lta bu la cho ma phyed du mthong pa'o //
NK100(the)011:1082: yang dag pa'i go lugs lnga ni /
NK100(the)011:1083: de la lnga las rang la nad par go ba ni /
NK100(the)011:1084: khams gsum 'khor bar khang mo che na zhugs /
NK100(the)011:1085: ma rigs pa'i thul tshan cig gon /
NK100(the)011:1086: bdag tu 'dzin pa'i pho mo gdon gyis gtab /
NK100(the)011:1087: 'dod chags kyi mo gdon tshan mo che gcig gis gzir /
NK100(the)011:1088: dug lnga dug gsum gyi lcong snying 'di tshabs su che la 'tshol bar daka'o //
NK100(the)011:1089: bla ma la de gso bar byed pa'i sman par go //
NK100(the)011:1090: gdams ngag la gso ba'i sman du /
NK100(the)011:1091: grogs mtshungs par spyod pa la nad g.yog tu /
NK100(the)011:1092: nan tan gdams ngag go nas spyod pa'i mi de nad sos par go bar byas la zhu'o //
NK100(the)011:1093: de ltar bla ma la brten pa la dgos pa ci yod na gsum las /
NK100(the)011:1094: dang po bla ma dam pa cig brten pas 'jig
NK100(the)011:1095: rten gyi kha na ma tho ba dang bcas pa
NK100(the)011:1097: bla ma mtshan nyid dang ldan pa ma nor ba cig brten pas /
NK100(the)011:1098: 'jig rten pas khyod kyi bla ma de gsha' ma
NK100(the)011:1099: med chos med mi zer ba'i dgos pa yod do
NK100(the)011:1100: // bcas pa dang kha na ma tho ba mi
NK100(the)011:1101: 'byungs pas rang yang bdag gi bla ma 'di yin
NK100(the)011:1102: par nges shes chen po skyes nas /
NK100(the)011:1103: dad pa la 'phel 'grib med pa'i dgos pa'o //
NK100(the)011:1104: dad pa la 'phel 'grib med par 'chi ka dang
NK100(the)011:1105: srid pa bar do dang tshe phyi ma la yang
NK100(the)011:1106: bla ma de'i snang ba 'char zhing bla ma des
NK100(the)011:1107: 'dren par mdzad pa'i dgos pa yod do //
NK100(the)011:1108: de ltar bla ma brten thabs de rnams kyang thos pa'i sgo nas ming bzung /
NK100(the)011:1109: de rnams dang ldan pa'i sgo nas brten dgos so //
NK100(the)011:1110: bla ma brten thabs gsal ba'i le'u ste /
NK100(the)011:1111: gsum pa'o ////de ltar sngon du 'gro ba'i sgo nas /
NK100(the)011:1112: dang po dal 'byor brtags pas thob par dka' ba de thob /
NK100(the)011:1113: dal 'byor thob pa des chos byed pa la dad pa dgos pas bar du dad pa bskyed /
NK100(the)011:1114: dad pa can lam sna 'dren pas bla ma brten thabs gsum sngon du 'gro bar bstan nas /
NK100(the)011:1115: da rang rgyud gdul te spyir yang dag par sangs
NK100(the)011:1116: rgyas kyi gsungs pa'i chos thams cad rgyud kyi gdul
NK100(the)011:1117: thabs su ma gyur pa med pas chos la bskur
NK100(the)011:1118: pa mi gdab pa nan tan du gal che gsung
NK100(the)011:1119: / de ru sh+ri si ngas rgyud gdul pa la drug tu gsung te bsgrang /
NK100(the)011:1120: dang po mi rtag pa rgyud la brten te rgyud gdul ba la bzhi ste bsgrang /
NK100(the)011:1122: snod bcud gnyis las 'dir bcud kyi sems can mi rtag pa gtsor ston /
NK100(the)011:1123: dang po snod mi rtags pa ston te /
NK100(the)011:1124: de yang mtha' mi rtag chags 'jig gnas stongs dang bcas so //
NK100(the)011:1125: de yang zhen pa log nas /
NK100(the)011:1126: snod kyi 'jig rten 'di yang mi rtag ste /
NK100(the)011:1127: snod kyi 'jig rten 'di ri rab lhun po dang /
NK100(the)011:1128: gser gyi ri bdun rol mtsho chen po bdun /
NK100(the)011:1129: gling bzhi gling phran lcags ri mu khyud kyang /
NK100(the)011:1130: 'jig pa'i dus nas bskal pa'i me byung bas /
NK100(the)011:1131: thal ba'i lhag ma tsam yang mi lus te //
NK100(the)011:1132: tha mar chu dang rlung gis 'jig pas na //
NK100(the)011:1133: brten cing nges pas 'dres rtags mi bzod //
NK100(the)011:1135: gnas skabs mi rtag ste dus bzhi 'gyur ldog dang bcas pa ni /
NK100(the)011:1137: dbyar dro skye la rgun grang skam pa dang //
NK100(the)011:1138: lo legs lo nyes than zhod nges pa med //
NK100(the)011:1139: rtsi thog ljon shing lo 'dab rgyas pa la //
NK100(the)011:1140: dus kyi drod bral rlung gis mi rtag go //
NK100(the)011:1141: rtag pa lags na ci phyir 'gyur zhing 'gro /
NK100(the)011:1143: nang bcud mi rtag pa ni /
NK100(the)011:1146: 'o na dpe ci dang 'dra bar mi rtag na /
NK100(the)011:1147: lus mi rtag g.yang pa'i sdong gogs 'dra ni /
NK100(the)011:1148: dper na g.yang sa cig na sdong po yod pa de 'gyel nas 'gro nges /
NK100(the)011:1149: de yang rlung la sogs pa'i rkyen gcig nam 'gyel cha med pa bzhin du /
NK100(the)011:1150: zag bcas kyi lus yang 'chi nges /
NK100(the)011:1151: rkyen gyi nam mchi cha med do //
NK100(the)011:1152: dbugs mi rtag la kha'i na bun 'dra ni /
NK100(the)011:1153: dper na la kha'i na bun de rkyen ser bu
NK100(the)011:1154: la sogs pa bag tsam cig gis yol nas 'gro
NK100(the)011:1155: ba bzhin du / srog rtsol gyi dbugs phar 'gro
NK100(the)011:1156: tshur 'gro 'di yang rkyen bag tsam cig gis chad
NK100(the)011:1158: yid mi rtag nam mkha'i glog dang 'dra ni /
NK100(the)011:1159: dper na nam mkha'i glog de skrems pa cig las mi 'ong pa bzhin du /
NK100(the)011:1160: yid 'di yang skad cig ma gnyis par mi sdod de 'gyur ba'o //
NK100(the)011:1161: tshe mi rtag rtsa kha'i zil pa 'dra ba ni /
NK100(the)011:1162: dper na rtsa kha'i zil pa de yang kya phrul che 'dug kyang /
NK100(the)011:1163: rlung la sogs pa'i rkyen bag tsam cig gis 'bog pa bzhin du /
NK100(the)011:1164: tshe 'di yang rkyen bag tsam cig gis 'gyur nas 'gro ba la tshegs med do //
NK100(the)011:1165: tshul gang gi sgo nas mi rtag ni /
NK100(the)011:1166: 'chi ba bzhi sbrag gis tshul gyis mi rtags /
NK100(the)011:1169: 'chi ba la cis kyang mi stongs pa /
NK100(the)011:1171: 'chi nges pa la bzhi ste bsgrang /
NK100(the)011:1172: sngar lus pa'i sems can med pa ni /
NK100(the)011:1174: snga ma skyes tshad ma shi nad //
NK100(the)011:1175: skyes nas shi bas ma tshugs pa'i //
NK100(the)011:1176: sa phyogs dag ni yod pa ma yin te //
NK100(the)011:1177: nam mkha' la med rgya mtsho gting na med //
NK100(the)011:1178: ri'i phug tu bros kyang yod ma yin //
NK100(the)011:1180: ri rab kyi khong seng na gnas pa'i drang srong mngon par shes pa dang ldan pa yang /
NK100(the)011:1182: phung po 'dus byas yin pa ni /
NK100(the)011:1185: gnas de rnyed par mi 'gyur te //
NK100(the)011:1186: 'dus byas thams cad mi rtag pas //
NK100(the)011:1187: mya ngan ma byed kun dga' bo //
NK100(the)011:1189: tshe skad cig mas mi sdod pa ni /
NK100(the)011:1190: nyin mtshan sdod pa yod med cing //
NK100(the)011:1191: tshe 'di mi rtag bsgrod gyur cing //
NK100(the)011:1192: snon pa gud na yod min pas //
NK100(the)011:1195: byas pa thams cad mi rtag pa gang gis 'thems /
NK100(the)011:1196: nam 'chi cha med pa'i chos ba bzhi ni bsgrang /
NK100(the)011:1197: tshe la nges pa med pa ni /
NK100(the)011:1199: sgra ma snyan na stong thub ste /
NK100(the)011:1200: gnyis na phyed phyed spangs pa'o //
NK100(the)011:1201: 'di na ma nges tha mar ni /
NK100(the)011:1202: lo bcu dang por dpag tu med //
NK100(the)011:1204: 'dzam bu gling pa'i tshe la nges pa med /
NK100(the)011:1205: dang po tshe lo dpag tu med pa /
NK100(the)011:1207: brgya pa'i dus su ston pa byon /
NK100(the)011:1209: sum cu par mu ge'i bskal pa /
NK100(the)011:1211: bcu par mtshon gyi bskal pa 'byung ngo //
NK100(the)011:1212: de'i dus su byams pa'i sprul pa byon nas //
NK100(the)011:1214: tha ma tshe lo brgyad khri bar 'gyur te /
NK100(the)011:1215: bar khug pa bac+wa brgyad du bartsi'o //
NK100(the)011:1216: de las da lta drug cu pa'i dus yin te /
NK100(the)011:1217: 'di rang la yang nges pa med do //
NK100(the)011:1218: mdo las tshe la nges pa med pa ni /
NK100(the)011:1221: kha cig dar la bab pa ni //
NK100(the)011:1222: kha cig rgas shing 'khogs pa na //
NK100(the)011:1223: smon pa'i shing thog ji bzhin du //
NK100(the)011:1224: thams cad srog gi 'chad par nges zhes so //
NK100(the)011:1225: lus la snying po med pa ni /
NK100(the)011:1226: bstan pa med cing mi rtag la //
NK100(the)011:1227: bstan pa med cing mi rtag g.yo //
NK100(the)011:1228: 'jim pa'i bum pa bzhin du 'jig pa can //
NK100(the)011:1229: gnyan ma 'dra yis 'di la ther zug med //
NK100(the)011:1237: mi gtsang ba'i rdzas kyis gang pa'o //
NK100(the)011:1239: gson pa'i rkyen ni rab 'ga' zhig /de dag nyid kyang 'chi ba'i rkyen /
NK100(the)011:1240: khams ni sprul gdug ma rungs pa /
NK100(the)011:1241: 'byung pa gcig la gcig brten nas /
NK100(the)011:1242: re re yang 'khrug par byed pa yis /
NK100(the)011:1245: yang 'chi ba'i rkyen du ma gyur gang yang med /
NK100(the)011:1246: lus 'di zas kyis 'chi yang rnangs nas 'chi /
NK100(the)011:1248: nad bzhi brgya rtsa gcig /gdon stong phrag brgyad cu /
NK100(the)011:1249: glo bur dang ye 'grogs sum brgya drug cus /
NK100(the)011:1251: snang ba brtag mi bzod ni /
NK100(the)011:1253: brtags na rang bzhin su yis rnyed //
NK100(the)011:1254: des na snang ba mi bden pas //
NK100(the)011:1255: 'chi ba'i dus las nges pa med //
NK100(the)011:1257: 'chi ba la cis kyang mi stongs pa'i chos bzhi bsgrang /
NK100(the)011:1258: brtsigs pa'i gnas kyis 'chi ba la mi gtong pa ni /
NK100(the)011:1259: 'chi bdag bdud kyis bzung nas ni /
NK100(the)011:1260: 'byung bzhi rims kyis thim dus su /
NK100(the)011:1261: mkhar ram btsan sa bzung nas ni /
NK100(the)011:1262: sgom bsdoms 'bos kyi bskor byas kyang /
NK100(the)011:1263: dar cig thub par mi 'gyur ro //
NK100(the)011:1265: 'brel pa'i gnyen gyis kyang mi gtongs pa ni /
NK100(the)011:1266: gnyen dang shes kyis mi gtongs te //
NK100(the)011:1267: bdag nyid mal na 'dug bzhin du //
NK100(the)011:1268: gnyen bshes mang pos mtha' bskor yang //
NK100(the)011:1269: srog gcod pa'i tsher ba ni //
NK100(the)011:1270: bdag nyid cig pus myong bar 'gyur //
NK100(the)011:1271: gshin rje'i pho nyas zin pa la //
NK100(the)011:1272: gnyen gyis ci phan bshes ci phan //
NK100(the)011:1273: zhes gnyen gyis tha ma bskor yang /
NK100(the)011:1274: zhag gcig gi shol yang mi thebs te /
NK100(the)011:1275: tha ma skar ma bzang ngan kyang gdab du med do //
NK100(the)011:1276: bsags pa'i nor rdzas kyis mi gtong /
NK100(the)011:1277: de yang nor dang rdzas kyis mi stongs te /
NK100(the)011:1278: rnyed pa mang pos thob 'gyur cing /
NK100(the)011:1279: yun rings dus su bde spyod kyang /
NK100(the)011:1280: chos pas bcom pa ji bzhin du /
NK100(the)011:1281: sgron me lag pa stong par 'gro zhes pas /
NK100(the)011:1282: bsags pa'i nor rdzas kyis 'chi bdag la bslur med do //
NK100(the)011:1283: rang gi lus kyis mi stongs pa ni /
NK100(the)011:1284: rang gi lus kyis mi stongs te //
NK100(the)011:1285: bdag gi 'di ltar bsos kyang ni //
NK100(the)011:1286: 'chi bdag brtse ba med pas yis //
NK100(the)011:1287: phrogs te bya dang khyi byin na //
NK100(the)011:1288: de tsho khyod kyis ci byar yod //
NK100(the)011:1291: dpa' rtsal che ba la sogs pa yon tan che yang bsdad du med do //
NK100(the)011:1292: 'chi ba rang gi dngos po'i chos bzhi ni bsgrang /
NK100(the)011:1293: bal gos kyi tha ma nyal ba ni /
NK100(the)011:1294: re gos leb gcig gis 'thum la khad /
NK100(the)011:1295: ro thag kyang cig mal du yong la khad pa'o //
NK100(the)011:1296: gnyen 'dun gyi tha mas bskor ba ni /
NK100(the)011:1297: tha ma bskor nas ngo shes sam zer te /
NK100(the)011:1298: chags pa bskyed pa las dgos pa med do //
NK100(the)011:1299: za chu'i tha ma ni dur rgyags kham gsum /
NK100(the)011:1300: gtam gyi tha ma ni kha chems tshig gsum smra ba'o //
NK100(the)011:1301: de ltar chings bzhi rnam grangs bcu drug po de /
NK100(the)011:1302: khar ston pas tshig yid la bsams pas sngug bsngal che ba las mi phan pas /
NK100(the)011:1303: rgyud la 'debs pa la de rnams kyi chings bzhi la /
NK100(the)011:1305: 'chi nges las chos bya bar bcad pa ni /
NK100(the)011:1306: 'chi nges las chos la mi bya ba'i thabs med de /
NK100(the)011:1309: bya lugs dbang po'i rim pa dang /
NK100(the)011:1310: sbyar te rgyas par bshad do //
NK100(the)011:1311: 'o na chos byed dang dgos te bu phog /bu mo bardzangasa /
NK100(the)011:1312: chos rgyags bsags la bya snyam na /
NK100(the)011:1313: nam 'chi cha med pas chos la phyi mthol mi gdab pa ni /
NK100(the)011:1314: do nub shi na sdug byed snyam pa byas la brtson 'grus cig skyed do //
NK100(the)011:1315: tshe 'di'i bya ba yang gal che snyam na /
NK100(the)011:1316: 'chi ba la cis kyang mi stongs pas /
NK100(the)011:1317: chos rkyen dbang du mi btang ba ni /
NK100(the)011:1318: rkyen ngos bzung la rkyen byung tsam na 'a ma
NK100(the)011:1319: bdag la cis kyang mi stongs par 'chi ba 'ong
NK100(the)011:1320: par 'dug pa cis kyang ga na phan snyam pas
NK100(the)011:1321: bskul te dge sbyor kho na bya'o //
NK100(the)011:1322: 'chi ba rang gi dngos po thog gsum nas gshin shing chos gsum dang ldan par bya ba ni /
NK100(the)011:1325: 'bring sgom thog /tha ma spyod thog go //
NK100(the)011:1330: rab lta thog nas 'chi bas mi 'jigs pa ni /
NK100(the)011:1331: dbang po rab lta ba phyogs med rtogs pas yon tan du phyogs zhen dang 'dzin pa grol te /
NK100(the)011:1332: ci yang chos nyid yin pas shi yang chog ma shi yang chog pa'o //
NK100(the)011:1333: 'bring sgom thog nas 'chi ste brod pa'i chos dang ldan pa ni /
NK100(the)011:1334: dbang po 'bring gsal stong 'dzin med du lus ngag yid gsum khong klod nas bsgoms pas /
NK100(the)011:1336: lhun grub chos sku'i sun ma brod pa ni /
NK100(the)011:1337: dbugs chad ma thog tu gzhi lhun grub rtog med cig skye'o //
NK100(the)011:1338: lta sgom bzang po'i skyel ma brod ni /
NK100(the)011:1339: sngar goms 'dres sngon du song pa de dang 'grogs nas 'agro'o //
NK100(the)011:1340: rang rtse gcig 'gro ba'i 'gron po brang ni /
NK100(the)011:1341: gdams ngag med pa 'chi kar 'tsher ba la /
NK100(the)011:1342: sgom pa dang ldan pa'i gang zag de da lta
NK100(the)011:1343: zag bcas kyi phung po 'di la na tsha 'dug
NK100(the)011:1344: ltogs 'khyags / shi na bde ba cig tu 'gro
NK100(the)011:1345: snyam nas rig pa rtse gcig tu 'gro ba bro
NK100(the)011:1346: ltogs 'khyags / pa'o // tha ma spyod thog nas 'chi ste /
NK100(the)011:1347: 'chi kar mi 'gyod pa'i chos dang ldan pa ni /
NK100(the)011:1351: rnam smin la btub tshad 'dzem dge ba la 'bad snyam nas ma 'gyod pa'o //
NK100(the)011:1352: de ltar mi rtag pa rgyud la skyes pa la phan yon nam dgos pa bzhi ste /
NK100(the)011:1354: 'chi ba mi rtag pa rgyud la bsgoms na dad pa cher 'gro ba'o //
NK100(the)011:1356: nam 'chi cha med pas le lor mi sdod pa'o //
NK100(the)011:1357: chags sdang myur du zhi bar byed pa ni /
NK100(the)011:1358: mi rtag pa rgyud la skyes pas chags sdang la
NK100(the)011:1359: ru ma med cing gnod pa skyel bar mthong nas
NK100(the)011:1360: / byed mi khom ste rang zhi ba'o //
NK100(the)011:1361: mnyam pa nyid kyi don rtogs sla ba ni /
NK100(the)011:1362: chags sdang myur du zhi bar byed pas so //
NK100(the)011:1363: de ltar mi rtag pa rgyud la bskyed de rang
NK100(the)011:1364: rgyud smu rengs se rengs pa 'di thul lam lta'o
NK100(the)011:1365: // des thul na 'di man chad mi dgos gsung ngo //
NK100(the)011:1366: des ma thul na glen pa rgyud la yang pa la /
NK100(the)011:1367: glen pa'i mdo bzhi ngo bo dgu brugs su ston te /
NK100(the)011:1369: bdag tu bzung pa'i glen pa gsum ni bsgrang /
NK100(the)011:1370: rang lus mi rtag sgyu ma la lhag pa'i bsnyen bskur byed pa shin du glen ni /
NK100(the)011:1371: rang lus snang yang 'jig pa'i chos can sgyu ma dang 'dra ba la /
NK100(the)011:1372: ma 'khyags ma ltogs tsam re gun la dgos te /
NK100(the)011:1373: gzhan las lhag pa'i zas gos sam phyi bsdar la sogs pa byed pa ni shin du glen no //
NK100(the)011:1374: mi lus 'di'i sdug bsngal phra mo mi bzod par /
NK100(the)011:1375: ngan song gsum gyi sdug bsngal bzod du re ba ni /
NK100(the)011:1376: tshe 'di'i ltogs 'khyags la sogs pa'i sdug bsngal bag tsam mi bzod par /
NK100(the)011:1379: dud 'gro glen lkugs kyi sdug bsngal bzod du re nas sdig pa byed pa glen no //
NK100(the)011:1380: sdug bsngal chen po nam 'ong cha med par /
NK100(the)011:1381: tshe 'di rtag par bzung nas nye re byed pa ni /
NK100(the)011:1382: sdug bsngal chen po ni gnad gcod do //
NK100(the)011:1383: de nam yang cha med par tshe 'di rtag pa
NK100(the)011:1384: bzung nas tshe 'di'i yo byad la sogs pa nya
NK100(the)011:1386: bdag gir bzung pa'i glen pa gsum ni /
NK100(the)011:1387: dgra mi rtag sgyu ma la /
NK100(the)011:1388: lhag pa'i zhe sdang byed pa'i shin tu glen pa ni /
NK100(the)011:1389: de yang dgra mtha' mi rtag 'chi /
NK100(the)011:1390: gnas skabs mi rtag dgra gnyen du 'gro ba la tshegs med /
NK100(the)011:1391: sgyu ma dang 'dra ba la thad ka'i ngo bsrung re dang 'ong srid kyang /
NK100(the)011:1392: lhag pa'i gdung sems byed pa ni 'dir sdug /phyi mar yi dwags su skye bas glen no //
NK100(the)011:1393: nor ni mtha' mi rtag mdzad /
NK100(the)011:1394: gnas skabs gtor zags la sogs pa 'ong pas sgyu ma dang 'dra ba la /
NK100(the)011:1395: nya ra en re dgos srid kyang /
NK100(the)011:1396: lhag pa'i zhen chags byed pa ni /
NK100(the)011:1397: 'dir sdug phyi mar yi dwags su skye bas glen no //
NK100(the)011:1398: bya byed las kyi glen pa gnyis ni /
NK100(the)011:1399: don yod dge ba bcu po ni /
NK100(the)011:1402: yid kyi gsum po de gzhung du spyad na don yod de /
NK100(the)011:1404: mthar thug sangs rgyas kyi rgyur 'gro ba la /
NK100(the)011:1405: de mi spyod par don med 'khrul pa med pa mi dge las la g.yengs pa glen no //
NK100(the)011:1406: mi lus gtsang ma rin chen ni /
NK100(the)011:1407: dal 'byor phun sum tshogs pa thob nas /
NK100(the)011:1408: bla na med pa'i byang chub kyis 'bras bu myur du mi sgrub par /
NK100(the)011:1409: rang gis rang sdug shom pa sdig pa'i las la spyod pa de shin tu glen no //
NK100(the)011:1410: mthar thug don la glen pa'i glen pa chen po ni /
NK100(the)011:1411: bden pa'i theg le cig ni /
NK100(the)011:1412: tshig gi tha snyad ci ltar brjod kyang /
NK100(the)011:1413: bden pa'i byang chub kyi sems thig le nyag gcig tu mi sdud par /
NK100(the)011:1414: mtshon pa tshig gi mtha' la zhen te /
NK100(the)011:1415: thos pa rgya mtsho byas kyang don go ma rnyed par tshig la zhen pa glen no //
NK100(the)011:1416: de ltar glen pa de rnams thos pa'i sgo nas ming bzung /
NK100(the)011:1417: bsam pas rang gi rgyud la 'dug gam mi 'dug bltas la /
NK100(the)011:1418: 'dug na spangs la rang rgyud rmu rengs su song pa 'di gdul lo //
NK100(the)011:1419: des ma thul na dka' ba rgyud la sgril te
NK100(the)011:1420: dka' ba rgyud la bsgril ba dka' ba dgu ni
NK100(the)011:1422: rgyud la bsgril ba gnyis las /
NK100(the)011:1423: dang po dka' ba dgu ni /
NK100(the)011:1424: dang po rdzogs pa chen po'i gdams ngag gi rten
NK100(the)011:1425: mi lus gtsang ma rin po che thob pa shin
NK100(the)011:1427: de la dka' rgyu cang yod dam mi 'di tsam 'dug pa snyam na /
NK100(the)011:1428: de dka' ba'i rgyu mtshan dang /
NK100(the)011:1429: sngon bsags pa'i las kyi rnam par smin pa gnyags ring po'i phyir ro //
NK100(the)011:1430: mi lus thob kyang bla ma dam pa dang 'jal ba shin tu dka' ste /
NK100(the)011:1431: de cang dka' 'am slob dpon 'di tsam 'dug pa gang mos la zhugs pas chog mod snyam na /
NK100(the)011:1432: de dka' ba'i rgyu mtshan du bar du gcod pa'i gegs grangs mang ba ste /
NK100(the)011:1433: bla ma dam pa dang mjal ba la /
NK100(the)011:1437: pha ma pha spun la sogs grangs mang pa'i phyir ro //
NK100(the)011:1438: bla ma dam pa dang mjal kyang zhabs nas 'degs pa shin tu dka' ste /
NK100(the)011:1439: cang dka' 'jam snyam na yod pa rta dang glang po 'bul /
NK100(the)011:1440: med pa kun kyang ci grub grub byed snyam na /
NK100(the)011:1441: rgyu mtshan du lan chags kyi bu lon dos drag pa mang ste /
NK100(the)011:1444: bu gnyen la sogs pa'i lan chags 'jal 'jal nas ma thegs pa /
NK100(the)011:1445: bla ma dam pa'i zhabs la bteg kyang zhabs thog 'di shes pas thongs pa shin tu dka' ste /
NK100(the)011:1446: de cang dka' 'am rang don la rlon pa dang khong yus mi byed snyam na /
NK100(the)011:1447: rgyu mtshan du ser sna'i mdud pa khong dam pa'i phyir ro //
NK100(the)011:1448: zhabs thog de shes pas thebs kyang bla ma dam
NK100(the)011:1449: pa'i chags phyir brtson zhing 'grus pa shin tu dka'
NK100(the)011:1450: / de yang dka' 'am gar pa bzhud du rang
NK100(the)011:1451: yang khres po phra la ring pa re grags nas
NK100(the)011:1452: / 'gro snyam na / rgyu mtshan du le le dang gtong snyoms gros zab pa'i phyir ro //
NK100(the)011:1453: bla ma dam pa'i chags phyir brtson zhing 'grus par byas kyang /
NK100(the)011:1454: gdams ngag go ba de shin tu dka' /
NK100(the)011:1455: de cang dka' 'am yun ring du byas pas khad kyis go snyam na /
NK100(the)011:1456: rgyu mtshan du rang rgyud la rtogs pa'i bag chags tshan che bas bsgribs pa'i phyir ro //
NK100(the)011:1457: bla ma dam pa'i gdams ngag gi yang go thog tu nus pa shin tu dka' /
NK100(the)011:1458: cang dka' 'am gdams ngag go na nyams su len nus snyam na /
NK100(the)011:1459: rgyu mtshan du sems can gyi las dbang kha drag pas nyams len mi nus pa'i phyir ro //
NK100(the)011:1460: go thog tu nus kyang thog tu brtan pa shin tu dka' /
NK100(the)011:1461: de cang dka' 'am nyams len nus na brten nas 'ong snyam na /
NK100(the)011:1462: rgyu mtshan du rig pa'i sems gya gyu mang pa'i phyir ro //
NK100(the)011:1463: de'i phyir bla na med pa'i byang chub thob par shin tu dka' /
NK100(the)011:1464: gong gi dka' ba brgyad 'phrang dam pa'i phyir ro //
NK100(the)011:1466: dang po mi lus rin po che thob par dka' ste /
NK100(the)011:1467: sngar thob na bla ma'i drung du 'dud /
NK100(the)011:1468: sngar ma thob na bsgrubs te thob par bya /
NK100(the)011:1470: mi lus rin po che thob par byed pa'i mtshan nyid dang /
NK100(the)011:1471: de bsgrub par bya ba'i thabs so //
NK100(the)011:1473: rgyal rigs dang rje rigs la sogs te /
NK100(the)011:1476: gzugs bzang zhing lta na mdzes pa /
NK100(the)011:1477: gzi che zil dang ldan zhing brjid che ba dang ldan pa /
NK100(the)011:1478: na tsha dkon pa tshe ring pa /
NK100(the)011:1479: 'byor pa yo byad phun sum 'tshogs pa /
NK100(the)011:1480: shes rab kyi kha lo yongs su byang pa'o //
NK100(the)011:1481: de sgrub par byed pa la sgrub thabs nyi shu
NK100(the)011:1482: rtsa gcig /bdun po re re la 'gal rkyen spangs
NK100(the)011:1484: cha mthun pa'i spyod lam bya ba'o //
NK100(the)011:1485: dang po rigs bzang pa la /
NK100(the)011:1486: 'gal ba'i rkyen du nyon mongs pa nga rgyal spang /
NK100(the)011:1488: cha mthun pa'i spyod pa dge sbyor kun la brtson par bya'o //
NK100(the)011:1489: gzugs bzang pa la nyon mongs pa khong khro spang /
NK100(the)011:1491: me tog gi mchod pa rtag tu dbul lo //
NK100(the)011:1492: gzi che ba la nyon mongs pa phrag dogs spang /
NK100(the)011:1494: bla ma la mos gus cher bya'o //
NK100(the)011:1498: sman gyi sbyin pa rtag tu dagye'o //
NK100(the)011:1499: tshe ring ba la srog gcod spang /
NK100(the)011:1502: 'byor ba'i yo byad phun sum tshogs pa la /
NK100(the)011:1503: rang gi ser sna gzhan gyi ma byin par len pa spang /
NK100(the)011:1504: med pa drug ldan gyi tshogs sog bya /
NK100(the)011:1505: kha dang lag gi sbyin pa rtag tu bagyi'o //
NK100(the)011:1507: yul la dmigs pa med pa /
NK100(the)011:1508: bsam pa la sel med pa /
NK100(the)011:1509: dad pa la 'gyur ldog med pa /
NK100(the)011:1510: rdzas la zhen pa med pa /
NK100(the)011:1511: rjes la zhen pa med pa mtha' la 'gyod pa med pa'o //
NK100(the)011:1512: shes rab yongs su byang ba la /
NK100(the)011:1513: gzhan shes rab gsum sbyong ba la bar chad mi bya /
NK100(the)011:1514: rang shes rab gsum la sbyang /
NK100(the)011:1515: mar me'i mchod pa rtag tu dbul lo //
NK100(the)011:1516: bla ma dam pa dang mjal ba dka' ste /
NK100(the)011:1517: sngar mjal na zhabs nas gdeg /ma mjal na bar chod kyi dbang du mi gtong /
NK100(the)011:1518: drung du phyin la mjal lo //
NK100(the)011:1520: sngar btegs na shes par thongs par bya /
NK100(the)011:1521: ma btegs na lan chags dbang du mi btang /
NK100(the)011:1522: mnyes pa phul la gdeg go //
NK100(the)011:1523: shes pas thongs pa dka' ste /
NK100(the)011:1524: sngar btang na chags phyir brtson zhing 'grus par bya /
NK100(the)011:1525: ma btang na ser sna'i dbang du mi btang /
NK100(the)011:1528: sngar brtson zhing 'grus na gdams ngag go bar bya /
NK100(the)011:1529: brtson zhing ma 'grus na le lo'i dbang du mi btang /
NK100(the)011:1532: gdams ngag go ba bka' ste /
NK100(the)011:1533: sngar go na go thog tu nus par bya /
NK100(the)011:1534: ma go na bag chags dbang du mi btang /
NK100(the)011:1536: go thog tu nus par dka' ste /
NK100(the)011:1537: sngar nus na nus thog brtan par bya /
NK100(the)011:1538: ma nus na bag chags dbang du btang /
NK100(the)011:1541: sngar brtan na 'bras bu thob par bya /
NK100(the)011:1542: ma brtan na gya gyu'i dbang du mi btang /
NK100(the)011:1547: des ma thul na chos dang mi ldan pa'i blo
NK100(the)011:1548: rigs bdun rgyud la bzlog ste rgyud gdul ba ni
NK100(the)011:1549: / de yang mi ldan pa'i blo rnam pa bdun la khyad par gyi dus bdun du /
NK100(the)011:1550: gdams pa'i rgya bdun gyis bzlog ste bsgrang ngo //
NK100(the)011:1551: 'dod ngan gyi blo rdzong zhen gang zag gi rigs ni /
NK100(the)011:1552: 'dod zhen ma grol bar kha tshig bzang po'i rdzong la zhen pa'o zhi /
NK100(the)011:1553: de zhen pa grol na lta ba bzang ba yin te /
NK100(the)011:1554: kha tshig dang lta ba ngan pas /
NK100(the)011:1555: lta ba ngan gyi spyang thag bcad pa'i dus so //
NK100(the)011:1557: chu shing gi snying po chos la bzlas la gdam pa ni /
NK100(the)011:1558: dper na chu shing la snying po med pa bzhin du /
NK100(the)011:1559: lta ba la phyogs 'dzin med pas /
NK100(the)011:1560: rdzong zhen la rang bzhin med par la bazla'o //
NK100(the)011:1561: rtsol zhen gyi blo rgyu snyoms gyis dal ba ni /
NK100(the)011:1563: mnyan nam byas pas shes rgya med /
NK100(the)011:1564: bsgoms sam byas pas nyams med la sogs pa'o //
NK100(the)011:1565: le lo can nges don mi 'grub pas /
NK100(the)011:1566: brtson 'grus kyi rta la bskyon pa'i dus so //
NK100(the)011:1567: gdams pa ni shing a 'bras kyi 'bras bu mi thob bas /
NK100(the)011:1568: brtson 'grus kyis gzhung bsrang dgos so //
NK100(the)011:1569: ma nges pa'i blo gya gyu can ni /
NK100(the)011:1571: nub te la la spyod mang po byed pa'o //
NK100(the)011:1572: des don mi 'grub pas ma nges pa'i lam 'phrang bcad pa'i dus so //
NK100(the)011:1573: gdams pa skyes bu bzong 'dzugs pa bzhin /
NK100(the)011:1574: chos gnad cig la nges shes skyed la nyams su len pa'o //
NK100(the)011:1575: zhe sdang gi blo rmu rgod lta bu ni /
NK100(the)011:1576: zhe sdang me ltar 'bar te rta mu rgod lta bu'o //
NK100(the)011:1577: zhe sdang gi me dbal gsod dgos pas zhe sdang gi me dbal gsad pa'i dus so //
NK100(the)011:1578: gdams pa lcags brdung 'gar gyi the thabs bzhin chos myur bar btags la ni /
NK100(the)011:1579: dper na 'gar la lcags brdung pa de drod ma
NK100(the)011:1580: yal ba la cig thog tu cig brtag pa bzhin
NK100(the)011:1581: du / zhe sdang lhangs tser skyes pa dang /
NK100(the)011:1582: de ma yal ba la chos nyid du ngo sprad de /
NK100(the)011:1583: de yang zhe sdang mda' ltar 'phang /
NK100(the)011:1584: gzhu lta dgug por bzhag ste /
NK100(the)011:1585: mda' ltar 'phang pa zhe sdang rang la bltas pas
NK100(the)011:1586: rang sems gsal ba'i rtsal zhe sdang la shar ba'o
NK100(the)011:1588: de bltas pas rang bzhin grub pa mi 'dug pa'o //
NK100(the)011:1590: de'i ngang la yid gsum khong klod nas bzhag pas
NK100(the)011:1591: nyon mongs pa zhe sdang gi thog nas gsal stong
NK100(the)011:1592: gnyis med kyi lta bsgom thun cig skye'o //
NK100(the)011:1594: gti mug gi blo rang bzhin gyis blun pa ni /
NK100(the)011:1595: mi go mi shes te mun thibs se ba de'o //
NK100(the)011:1596: des mi phan te gti mug gi mun khang btib pa'o //
NK100(the)011:1597: gdams pa nad pa'i kha zas bzhin chos gar mos pa drangs la ni /
NK100(the)011:1598: dper na nad g.yog mkhas pas kha zas chung la
NK100(the)011:1599: mang pa yang yad btab pas gang rung gcig gi
NK100(the)011:1600: dang ka phyed pa bzhin du /
NK100(the)011:1601: gdams ngag gi sna mang du btab pas gang rung cig go nas 'ong ngo //
NK100(the)011:1602: phyogs zhen gyi blor mur lhungs pa ni /
NK100(the)011:1603: rang gi chos la zhen nas gzhan la dbang bskur pa 'debs pa'o //
NK100(the)011:1604: de rang gi chos phyogs cig la zhan pas don la ser sna'i mdud pa dbrel ba'i dus so //
NK100(the)011:1605: gdam pa bya khu byug gi skad bzhin chos rnam grangs ni /
NK100(the)011:1606: dper na bya khu byug la skad zhen dgrol lo //
NK100(the)011:1607: tshig 'phyos kyi blo kha lo de yongs su byang ba ni /
NK100(the)011:1608: don go ma rnyed tshig shin tu byang pa'o //
NK100(the)011:1609: de don go med pas rnam par rtog pa'i rlung 'phyos pa yin pas /
NK100(the)011:1610: rnam par rtog pa'i rlung bcing pa'i dus su /
NK100(the)011:1612: byis pa la zla ba mtshon pa bzhin chos nyams pa'o //
NK100(the)011:1613: dper na byis pa la zla ba mtshon pa de
NK100(the)011:1614: 'dzub mo la mig bkris nas bstan pas mthong ba
NK100(the)011:1615: bzhin du / kho rang gi tshig de la brten
NK100(the)011:1616: don nyams kyi go ba cig brtsal gyi gdam pa'o
NK100(the)011:1617: bzhin du / // de ltar mi ldan pa'i blo de rnams bzlog ste thul lam blta'o //
NK100(the)011:1618: des ma thul nas ldan pa'i shes rab rgyud la
NK100(the)011:1619: skye tshul ni thos pa las gyur pa'i shes rab
NK100(the)011:1620: ni / ming la gdam pa'i ste tshig 'dzin /
NK100(the)011:1621: bsam pa las gyur pa'i shes rab ni /
NK100(the)011:1622: ming don gnyis ka la gdam pa ste /
NK100(the)011:1623: tshig don sbrel bsam mno btang ngo //
NK100(the)011:1624: sgom pa las gyur pa'i shes rab ni /
NK100(the)011:1625: don la gdam pa ste ma yengs par glod pa'o //
NK100(the)011:1626: shes rab gsum po rgyud la sbyang lugs gsum ste bsgrang /
NK100(the)011:1627: dang po dgos pa rgyu 'bras kyi tshul du sbyar ba la gnyis las /
NK100(the)011:1628: dang po dgos pa'i tshul cha la gsum /
NK100(the)011:1629: thos pa las gyur pa'i shes rab skom pa chu 'tshol ba lta bu cig dgos pa ni /
NK100(the)011:1630: dper na skom pa'i mi de lus ngag yid gsum gyis dka' las kyis chu 'tshol ba bzhin du /
NK100(the)011:1631: thos pa byed pa de yang lus ngag yid gsum gyi dka' las kyi chu 'tshol ba bzhin du /
NK100(the)011:1632: thos pa'i phyogs su byed pa'o //
NK100(the)011:1633: bsam pa las gyur pa'i shes rab 'grangs par zas za ba lta bu /
NK100(the)011:1634: dper na ltogs pa zas za ba de ma 'grangs bar du za ba bzhin du /
NK100(the)011:1635: gros thag ma chod bar du sems pa'o //
NK100(the)011:1636: bsgom pa las gyur pa'i shes rab ngal dub gnyid logs pa ni /
NK100(the)011:1637: dper na ngal zhing dub pa gnyid du rang dbang med par 'gro ba bzhin du /
NK100(the)011:1638: shes rab gnyis po la rgyud 'byongs pas stong gsal gyi ngang la ngang gis gnas so //
NK100(the)011:1639: gnyis pa rgyu 'bras kyi tshul gsum /
NK100(the)011:1640: thos pa la gyur pa'i shes rab nam mkha' la char bab pa lta bu ni /
NK100(the)011:1641: yang dang yang du bstud cing bya'o //
NK100(the)011:1642: de byas pas bsam pa las gyur pa'i shes rab
NK100(the)011:1643: sa gzhi la rtsi thog skyes pa lta bu cig
NK100(the)011:1644: skye'o // de byas pas bsgoms pa las gyur pa'i
NK100(the)011:1645: shes rab rtsi thog las 'bras bu smin pa lta
NK100(the)011:1646: skye'o // bur smin no // bye brag zlog skye'i tshul la gnyis /
NK100(the)011:1647: dang po mi ldan pa'i blo rgyud zlog tshul la gsum /
NK100(the)011:1648: thos pa las gyur pa'i shes rab kyis snod gzhogs ral zlog ni /
NK100(the)011:1649: dper na snod gzhogs ral cig tu ci blugs kyang phyed las ma chags /
NK100(the)011:1650: de cis lan na gzhogs ral bas lan no //
NK100(the)011:1651: de la thabs ni gzhogs ral po gso ba bzhin du /
NK100(the)011:1652: thos pa byas pas phyed ma zin pa'i gzhogs ral de /
NK100(the)011:1653: thos pa bskyar bas phyed po de zin te bzlogs pa'o //
NK100(the)011:1654: bsam pa las gyur pa'i shes rab kyis snod zhabs brdol bzlog pa ni /
NK100(the)011:1655: dper na snod zhabs brdol du ci blugs kyang nang du mi chags /
NK100(the)011:1656: ci lan na zhabs brdol de la thabs ni zhabs 'gegs pa bzhin du /
NK100(the)011:1657: thos pa'i dus su zin kyang rjed nas zhabs rdol ba de /
NK100(the)011:1658: bsam pas mi brjod de de las bzlog go //
NK100(the)011:1659: sgom pa las gyur pa'i shes rab kyis snod kha bub las bzlog ni /
NK100(the)011:1660: dper na snod kha sbub tu nang du ci blugs
NK100(the)011:1661: kyang phyir kha le las nang cig kyang mi 'gro
NK100(the)011:1662: / de cis lan na kha sbub pas lan /
NK100(the)011:1663: thabs ni kha 'gyel ba bzhin du /
NK100(the)011:1664: thos bsam byas kyang nang du rgyud la ye ma 'byar ba de /
NK100(the)011:1665: bsgoms pas rang rgyud grol te 'bras bu thob bo //
NK100(the)011:1666: ldan pa'i shes rab rgyud la skye tshul gsum thos
NK100(the)011:1667: pa las gyur pa'i shes rab rno la ngar btags
NK100(the)011:1669: dper na lcags sna dgu la sogs pa la brdungs
NK100(the)011:1670: pa'i zhun thar dang ral gri ye nas rno ba
NK100(the)011:1671: la ngar btags pas btab tshad chod pa bzhin du
NK100(the)011:1672: / shes rab dang ldan pa la thos pa byas
NK100(the)011:1673: pas btab tshad chod de don ji lta ba bzhin
NK100(the)011:1674: / du rtogs pa'o // bsam pa las gyur pa'i
NK100(the)011:1675: shes rab spang la me mched pa'i tshul du skye
NK100(the)011:1676: / du rtogs pa'o // ni / dper na spang
NK100(the)011:1677: la me chung ba las chen por mched pa bzhin
NK100(the)011:1678: / du rtogs pa'o // ni / du / bsam pas tshig don gnyis ka mched do //
NK100(the)011:1679: bsgom pa las gyur pa'i shes rab yid bzhin gyi
NK100(the)011:1680: nor bu rin po che la dgos 'dod 'byung pa'i
NK100(the)011:1681: tshul ni / dper na nor bu las dgos 'dod 'byung ba bzhin du /
NK100(the)011:1682: bsgoms pas 'di ni drod rtags dang mthar thug 'bras bu la sogs pa 'byung ngo //
NK100(the)011:1683: shes rab gsum po rgyud la sbyangs pa'i dgos pa la gsum /
NK100(the)011:1684: thos pa las gyur pa'i shes rab la rgyud 'byongs na /
NK100(the)011:1685: 'gro ba 'dren pa'i chos 'chad pa la nyam mi nga ba'i dgos pa'i /
NK100(the)011:1686: bsam pa las gyur pa'i shes rab la rgyud 'byongs na /
NK100(the)011:1687: phyir rgol ba'i rtsod pa la nyam mi nga ba'i dgos pa /
NK100(the)011:1688: bsgoms pa las gyur pa'i shes rab la rgyud 'byongs na /
NK100(the)011:1689: byang chub kyi 'bras bu la nyam mi nga ba'i dgos pa'o //
NK100(the)011:1690: de ltar gsum po de bskyed la rgyud thul lam blta'o //
NK100(the)011:1691: des ma thul na nan tan gyi gdams ngag rgyud la mnan pa la gsum bsgrang /
NK100(the)011:1692: log par lta ba khyer bzhi ni /
NK100(the)011:1693: slob dpon go 'dris khyer ba ni /
NK100(the)011:1694: bla ma dang 'dris grags pas mos gus chung du song pa'o //
NK100(the)011:1695: gdams ngag sna dred khyer ba ni /
NK100(the)011:1696: yang yang mnyan gyi rgyud la ma sbyar bas dred pas phan ma thogs pa'o //
NK100(the)011:1697: dad pa snod rnyings khyer ba ni /
NK100(the)011:1698: dad pa yod pa dge sbyor ma byas pas dad pa chung du song mi tshe zad pa'o //
NK100(the)011:1699: dam tshig tshod yod khyer ba ni /
NK100(the)011:1700: spyir gsang sngags pa la dam tshig sa ma ya 'bum sde /
NK100(the)011:1701: de las bsdus pa sum brgya drug cu /
NK100(the)011:1702: de las bsdus pas nyer lnga'am /
NK100(the)011:1704: de'i nang nas phra mo re nyams pa la des
NK100(the)011:1705: ci yang mi nyes snyam nas tshod yod khyer ba'o
NK100(the)011:1707: bla ma go 'dris khyer du mi gzhug /dad gus bya bu ta'i 'du shes bskyed do //
NK100(the)011:1708: man ngag la nan tan byas nyams su blang ngo //
NK100(the)011:1709: dad pa'i stobs kyis dge sbyor la nan tan bskyed do //
NK100(the)011:1710: dam tshig phra ba nas 'dzem par bya'o //
NK100(the)011:1711: rgyud mdzes pa'i chas bzhi ni /
NK100(the)011:1712: chos mdzad rnams kyis rgyud dman pa'i chus su bcug pa ni /
NK100(the)011:1713: dman cha bzung des ci byed na /
NK100(the)011:1714: 'jig rten pa'i grags pa gzhom mo //
NK100(the)011:1715: rgyud thos bsam gyi chas su bcug la ni /
NK100(the)011:1717: des ci byed na lta spyod kyi sgro 'dog bcad do //
NK100(the)011:1718: rgyud dad pa'i chas su bcug pa ni /
NK100(the)011:1719: mos pa dad pa yid ches pa'o //
NK100(the)011:1720: ci byed na 'chi ba mi rtag pa rjes su dran par bya'o //
NK100(the)011:1721: rgyud brtson 'grus kyi chas su bcug la ni /
NK100(the)011:1724: dam pa'i gdams ngag nye bar nyams su blangs pa'o //
NK100(the)011:1725: rgyud bsring pa las kyi 'phro dgu mthud pa ni /
NK100(the)011:1726: rang gi yo byad phun 'tshogs pa bya ba'i phyir /
NK100(the)011:1727: tshogs bsags pa rgyun bsrings pas las kyi 'phro mthud pa ni /
NK100(the)011:1728: nor yod pa rgyu mtshan du zhog la tshogs sogs /
NK100(the)011:1729: de ci'i phyir sdus pa las /
NK100(the)011:1730: byang chub sems dpa'i sbyin pas yi dwags 'gro ba gcod /
NK100(the)011:1731: dbul ba dang ni de bzhin nyon mongs thams cad sel /
NK100(the)011:1732: spyod tshe longs spyod mtha' yas rgyas pa thob par 'gyur /
NK100(the)011:1734: med pas med pa rgyu mtshan du zhog la tshogs sogs /
NK100(the)011:1736: dbul 'phongs bzhin ngan lus la nad mngas rnams /
NK100(the)011:1737: snga ma'i rnam smin lags pas gzhan la spus ma che /
NK100(the)011:1738: ces pas tshogs gang 'byor du bsag go //
NK100(the)011:1739: bla ma dam pa dang mjal bar bya ba'i phyir /
NK100(the)011:1740: bla ma la mos shing gus pa rgyun bsrings pas las kyi 'phro 'thud ni /
NK100(the)011:1741: tshe 'di la bla ma la gus pa byas pas phyi ma la mjal bas gus pa bya'o //
NK100(the)011:1742: rdzogs pa chen po'i go zhing snod du rung par bya'i phyir /
NK100(the)011:1743: rdzogs pa chen po'i don la mos shing gus pa rgyun bsrings pas las kyi 'phro mthud ni /
NK100(the)011:1744: tshe 'di la theg pa thams cad kyi yang rtse
NK100(the)011:1745: rdzogs pa chen po la mos gus byas pas phyi
NK100(the)011:1747: rang gi sems las su rung bar bya ba'i phyir /
NK100(the)011:1748: ting nge 'dzin rgyun bsrings pas las kyi 'phro mthud ni /
NK100(the)011:1749: de yang tshe rabs thog ma med pa nas 'khor bar 'khyams pa cis lan na /
NK100(the)011:1750: rang sems las su ma rung pas lan te /
NK100(the)011:1751: da rang sems las su rung par bya ba'i phyir /
NK100(the)011:1753: de yang ting na chos nyid /
NK100(the)011:1754: 'dzin na bying rmugs rgod yengs kyi dbang du ma shor bar bya'o //
NK100(the)011:1755: de rgyun bsrings la 'phro mthud do //
NK100(the)011:1756: de ltar bzhi po 'di yang tshe 'di la lta sgom mngon du ma gyur na /
NK100(the)011:1757: 'phro 'thud pa shin tu gal che bas nyams su blang dgos so //
NK100(the)011:1758: de ltar bzhi gsum bcu gnyis po 'di yang thos pa'i sgo nas ming bzung /
NK100(the)011:1759: de la rtog dpyod zhib tu byas la nyams su blang ste /
NK100(the)011:1760: rang rgyud rmu rengs se rengs 'di gdul lo //
NK100(the)011:1761: rang rgyud gdul thabs gsal bar byed pa'i le'u ste
NK100(the)011:1762: bzhi pa'o ////rnyed dka' dal 'byor rin chen thob dus
NK100(the)011:1763: 'dir // rang ngo shes shing 'khrul pa zlog dgos pas //
NK100(the)011:1764: de'i don ngo sprod snyan rgyud rin po che'i //
NK100(the)011:1765: thun mong gsal bar byed pa'i ting ka 'di //
NK100(the)011:1766: spyi dang mi 'gal bla ma'i gsung sgros dag /mi 'gal tsam du dbus pa rta yis bris //
NK100(the)011:1767: nongs 'khrul mchis na bla ma lha la bshags //
NK100(the)011:1768: rjes 'jug mos pa bstan pa'i sgron mer shog //
NK100(the)011:1769: thun mong spyi gsal bar byed pa //
NK100(the)011:1770: rta jo yes kyis bkod pa /
